WEBVTT

00:00:14.750 --> 00:00:16.041
You are a strong woman.

00:00:16.125 --> 00:00:17.250
You can do it, darling!

00:00:17.333 --> 00:00:18.416
Come on.

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:19.333
Push it.

00:00:22.208 --> 00:00:24.291
Hold on, ma'am.
Just a little bit more.

00:00:24.375 --> 00:00:25.750
Nine centimeters dilated.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:28.291
We can see the head, sir.

00:00:31.708 --> 00:00:34.166
Honey!

00:00:34.875 --> 00:00:36.583
-Honey--
-Please, hold on.

00:00:36.666 --> 00:00:38.625
Honey, come here.

00:00:38.708 --> 00:00:39.791
-Yes, I'm here.
-Honey…

00:00:43.208 --> 00:00:44.583
What should we do?

00:00:44.666 --> 00:00:46.791
No more dialogue.
Andara hasn't sent it yet.

00:00:47.625 --> 00:00:49.500
-We haven't received any?
-No, none.

00:00:49.583 --> 00:00:51.541
-Regulate your breathing.
-Now, breathe…

00:00:52.583 --> 00:00:53.958
Take a breath.

00:00:54.041 --> 00:00:56.000
Just a little more, keep breathing.

00:00:56.083 --> 00:00:57.125
Hold on, ma'am.

00:00:57.208 --> 00:00:59.375
-Hold on. Take a breath.
-Relax.

00:00:59.458 --> 00:01:00.875
Hurry, I have a deadline!

00:01:00.958 --> 00:01:02.333
Take a breath.

00:01:09.291 --> 00:01:11.625
Who's calling?

00:01:12.541 --> 00:01:14.166
Sastra, the director.

00:01:14.250 --> 00:01:16.083
Pick it up. Just pick it up!

00:01:16.166 --> 00:01:17.041
-You sure?
-Yes!

00:01:17.125 --> 00:01:20.458
I'm sorry, please don't.
We're in active labor now.

00:01:20.541 --> 00:01:22.958
We can see the head.
Please be patient.

00:01:23.041 --> 00:01:24.125
Please focus, okay?

00:01:24.208 --> 00:01:25.708
-So sorry, Doc.
-Don't.

00:01:25.791 --> 00:01:27.666
-This is urgent, Doc. So urgent!
-Yeah.

00:01:27.750 --> 00:01:29.375
-Pick it up!
-Hold on. Be patient.

00:01:29.458 --> 00:01:31.958
-Put it here! Hello, hello, hello.
-Don't pick…

00:01:32.041 --> 00:01:33.166
Yes, sir?

00:01:33.250 --> 00:01:35.416
What happened to
the haunted house scene?

00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:37.750
Are we putting the devil child
into the scene?

00:01:37.833 --> 00:01:41.625
Put him back in!

00:01:41.708 --> 00:01:43.416
Write it down. Put him back in.

00:01:44.458 --> 00:01:47.250
Ma'am, the head is already visible.

00:01:47.333 --> 00:01:48.333
It's almost here.

00:01:48.416 --> 00:01:49.416
No way back in.

00:01:49.500 --> 00:01:50.750
We can't return a baby.

00:01:50.833 --> 00:01:52.000
We can't do it.

00:01:52.083 --> 00:01:53.458
No, it's about work.

00:01:53.541 --> 00:01:55.083
Okay, sure.

00:01:55.625 --> 00:01:56.916
What about the reaction?

00:01:58.208 --> 00:01:59.500
Run away!

00:01:59.583 --> 00:02:02.458
-The devil's child!
-What?

00:02:02.541 --> 00:02:06.250
Oh, my God, ma'am. This is yours
and your husband's, not the devil's child.

00:02:06.333 --> 00:02:09.125
Andara, where the hell are you?

00:02:09.208 --> 00:02:10.583
I'm in labor.

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:22.166
She's in labor! She's giving birth!

00:02:22.250 --> 00:02:23.416
New baby arrived!

00:02:29.208 --> 00:02:30.708
My grandchild was just born!

00:02:30.791 --> 00:02:32.958
What is it?
My grandchild was born.

00:02:33.041 --> 00:02:33.958
Fill out the form.

00:02:34.041 --> 00:02:35.458
That's not important.

00:02:36.583 --> 00:02:39.166
Raja Partogi Gultom,
the one who gave birth recently.

00:02:39.250 --> 00:02:41.000
What are you doing? Hurry up!

00:02:41.083 --> 00:02:43.041
-Counter 1 over there.
-It's you.

00:02:43.125 --> 00:02:44.333
It's all because of you.

00:02:44.416 --> 00:02:47.000
You make things difficult.

00:02:47.083 --> 00:02:48.416
You ugly thing!

00:02:53.291 --> 00:02:55.583
Congratulations, here's your baby.

00:02:55.666 --> 00:02:57.125
A healthy boy.

00:02:57.208 --> 00:02:59.375
All his organs are perfect.

00:03:00.083 --> 00:03:01.458
You can hold him.

00:03:01.541 --> 00:03:03.666
But, please don't put him back in.

00:03:04.250 --> 00:03:06.583
-Congratulations, ma'am.
-Thank you, Doctor.

00:03:06.666 --> 00:03:08.916
Thank you, nurse.

00:03:15.333 --> 00:03:19.458
Thank you, dear.
Thank God.

00:03:27.083 --> 00:03:28.375
Which one?

00:03:28.458 --> 00:03:30.416
Which one is my grandchild?

00:03:30.916 --> 00:03:31.916
This one?

00:03:32.541 --> 00:03:33.708
Or this one?

00:03:33.791 --> 00:03:35.958
Look at his face.
This one looks like Raja.

00:03:37.083 --> 00:03:38.833
Which one?
Read the name for me!

00:03:38.916 --> 00:03:39.791
Wait a minute.

00:03:40.333 --> 00:03:41.416
This one.

00:03:41.500 --> 00:03:45.916
Mrs. Andara Respati,
Mr. Raja Partogi Gultom.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:47.541
But there's no baby there.

00:03:47.625 --> 00:03:50.000
Where's my grandchild?

00:03:50.666 --> 00:03:52.416
-My grandchild is missing.
-What?

00:03:52.500 --> 00:03:55.916
-My grandchild is missing!
-No, he's not missing.

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:57.208
Police!

00:03:57.291 --> 00:03:59.625
-My grandchild is missing!
-Stop making noise!

00:03:59.708 --> 00:04:01.291
My grandchild is missing!

00:04:01.375 --> 00:04:04.083
Maybe the mother is breastfeeding
the baby in the room.

00:04:05.208 --> 00:04:07.500
Why are you so slow?

00:04:07.583 --> 00:04:08.583
Just relax, will you?

00:04:09.625 --> 00:04:10.541
This is it.

00:04:10.625 --> 00:04:12.458
-Is this the right room?
-Yes, it is.

00:04:13.083 --> 00:04:14.250
Move aside.

00:04:14.333 --> 00:04:15.416
Where's my grandchild?

00:04:15.500 --> 00:04:16.541
-Mom.
-Where?

00:04:16.625 --> 00:04:18.000
-It's a boy.
-Mom.

00:04:18.083 --> 00:04:19.291
You!

00:04:19.375 --> 00:04:21.416
Where is your brain?

00:04:21.500 --> 00:04:23.083
You just gave birth.

00:04:23.166 --> 00:04:25.041
You should look after your child first.

00:04:25.125 --> 00:04:26.791
I'll trash this laptop eventually!

00:04:26.875 --> 00:04:28.541
-What are you?
-Mom, stop.

00:04:28.625 --> 00:04:29.458
Move aside!

00:04:30.916 --> 00:04:33.500
-Congratulations, Andara.
-Thank you, Auntie.

00:04:36.125 --> 00:04:37.208
Move your hands away.

00:04:37.916 --> 00:04:40.750
-What kind of person are you?
-Mom.

00:04:41.375 --> 00:04:43.000
Shut up.

00:04:43.083 --> 00:04:44.291
She has to understand.

00:04:44.875 --> 00:04:46.000
I'm surprised.

00:04:46.083 --> 00:04:51.250
She just gave birth, but she's working
instead of resting.

00:04:53.666 --> 00:04:57.000
Raja, please don't forget.

00:04:58.750 --> 00:05:00.250
Your father's wish.

00:05:01.416 --> 00:05:03.000
You have to name him Nicholas,

00:05:03.083 --> 00:05:03.916
okay, son?

00:05:08.541 --> 00:05:09.916
Yes, Mom.

00:05:14.250 --> 00:05:16.958
My grandson is so handsome!

00:05:17.041 --> 00:05:18.708
You look just like your grandpa.

00:05:26.875 --> 00:05:28.916
-Yes.
-Excuse me.

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:32.041
I'm returning the things she threw.

00:05:32.125 --> 00:05:34.500
-Okay.
-This one as well.

00:05:34.583 --> 00:05:36.958
-Thank you.
-You're welcome.

00:05:40.708 --> 00:05:42.916
Sis, your bun.

00:05:43.833 --> 00:05:45.125
Where did you get it from?

00:05:45.625 --> 00:05:48.083
-You threw it away earlier.
-Just put it on my head.

00:05:51.041 --> 00:05:52.375
Don't move.

00:05:54.291 --> 00:05:55.958
Why does it smell? What is it?

00:05:56.041 --> 00:05:57.291
Is that from your hands?

00:05:57.375 --> 00:05:59.625
My hands don't smell.

00:05:59.708 --> 00:06:01.291
How dare you!

00:06:01.375 --> 00:06:02.416
No, it doesn't smell.

00:06:02.500 --> 00:06:05.250
Hey, how dare you!
Or I'll grab your hair.

00:06:54.916 --> 00:06:56.416
Blow out the candle

00:06:56.500 --> 00:06:58.041
Blow out the candle

00:06:58.125 --> 00:07:00.916
Blow out the candles right now

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:06.125
Right now, right now

00:07:10.208 --> 00:07:11.375
Happy Birthday.

00:07:11.458 --> 00:07:13.958
-Happy Birthday!
-Happy Birthday!

00:07:14.791 --> 00:07:16.041
Awesome!

00:07:16.125 --> 00:07:18.750
Now, let's take a picture!

00:07:18.833 --> 00:07:19.958
Let's do it.

00:07:20.041 --> 00:07:22.458
-Let's get ready.
-Face this way.

00:07:22.541 --> 00:07:24.000
One moment my phone.

00:07:24.083 --> 00:07:26.125
Let's take a picture.

00:07:26.208 --> 00:07:27.916
What happened?

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:29.375
Come on, let's make it good.

00:07:30.041 --> 00:07:32.208
Gather to the middle.

00:07:32.875 --> 00:07:33.750
Everyone.

00:07:33.833 --> 00:07:36.333
Let's pose like this.

00:07:36.416 --> 00:07:38.250
Let's do it everyone.

00:07:38.333 --> 00:07:39.875
What's this outfit?

00:07:39.958 --> 00:07:41.541
You're wearing the wrong costume.

00:07:41.625 --> 00:07:42.666
This is a frog party.

00:07:42.750 --> 00:07:46.083
-We're using frog costumes.
-Well, you don't look like a frog.

00:07:46.166 --> 00:07:49.458
-Look at our costumes.
-Come on, look at Nicho.

00:07:50.375 --> 00:07:53.208
Go away! You need to separate yourself
from us.

00:07:53.291 --> 00:07:55.625
-Switch!
-You get in there.

00:07:55.708 --> 00:07:57.625
Now it's your turn. Quick!

00:07:57.708 --> 00:07:59.583
-All green now.
-Okay, okay.

00:07:59.666 --> 00:08:02.125
Move a bit,
so I can get in the picture.

00:08:02.208 --> 00:08:04.833
That's more like it.

00:08:04.916 --> 00:08:05.791
I'll count.

00:08:05.875 --> 00:08:08.333
One, two, three.

00:08:08.875 --> 00:08:10.958
One, two, three.

00:08:11.041 --> 00:08:13.166
-You're the very froggy one, smile.
-Shut up!

00:08:13.250 --> 00:08:16.125
One, two, three.

00:08:16.208 --> 00:08:17.416
That's enough.

00:08:17.500 --> 00:08:19.250
Go to take more pictures with Nicho.

00:08:20.458 --> 00:08:22.041
Here's your phone.

00:08:22.125 --> 00:08:23.375
What do you mean by that?

00:08:23.958 --> 00:08:26.500
-Look, these are our pictures.
-Come here, Grandma.

00:08:26.583 --> 00:08:29.375
-Go on take more pictures with Mom.
-Let's do it.

00:08:29.458 --> 00:08:31.208
Why is the event so dull?

00:08:31.291 --> 00:08:33.833
Not festive, not crowded.

00:08:33.916 --> 00:08:35.083
Like in the forest.

00:08:35.166 --> 00:08:37.333
Nicho's mom, you work in entertainment.

00:08:37.833 --> 00:08:40.375
You should invite all the models
and actress.

00:08:40.458 --> 00:08:41.708
Not too quiet like this.

00:08:42.625 --> 00:08:43.958
That's enough, Mom.

00:08:44.041 --> 00:08:46.041
Let this be a family event.

00:08:46.125 --> 00:08:47.583
No need to be so hedonistic.

00:08:48.125 --> 00:08:49.333
But remember, Raja.

00:08:49.416 --> 00:08:52.666
For my birthday,
I want to throw a huge party.

00:08:52.750 --> 00:08:54.666
Not like this. As quiet as a grave.

00:08:54.750 --> 00:08:56.208
Hey, Nicho's mom.

00:08:56.291 --> 00:08:57.500
Pay it all back.

00:08:57.583 --> 00:09:00.500
The cooking gas, electricity expenses.
Okay?

00:09:00.583 --> 00:09:02.083
Pay everything back.

00:09:02.625 --> 00:09:03.625
Yes, Mom.

00:09:03.708 --> 00:09:05.666
For my body lotion as well.

00:09:05.750 --> 00:09:07.000
My skin is getting dry.

00:09:07.083 --> 00:09:09.291
There's no need for you
to use body lotion.

00:09:09.375 --> 00:09:11.041
Just let your skin flake.

00:09:11.125 --> 00:09:14.000
Or just use old cooking oil.

00:09:14.083 --> 00:09:17.041
Don't forget that your hair
is full of lice.

00:09:17.125 --> 00:09:18.625
You can use lamp oil, okay?

00:09:24.041 --> 00:09:25.250
So annoying.

00:09:26.833 --> 00:09:28.041
I'm not happy about this!

00:09:38.708 --> 00:09:39.958
A lot of work, dear?

00:09:44.708 --> 00:09:45.916
Honey…

00:09:47.541 --> 00:09:49.666
When can we have our own house?

00:09:52.166 --> 00:09:54.083
I want to be free.

00:09:54.166 --> 00:09:57.250
I don't want to be constantly
controlled by your mother.

00:09:58.875 --> 00:10:02.208
Even Nicho's birthday,
your mother organized that, too.

00:10:03.125 --> 00:10:04.166
I know.

00:10:04.250 --> 00:10:06.791
Do we have to be frogs every year?

00:10:08.458 --> 00:10:14.541
I'm Nicho's mother. I want to organize
my son's birthday party in my own way.

00:10:16.333 --> 00:10:18.625
I know what you mean.

00:10:19.583 --> 00:10:22.375
But Nicho also likes that costume.

00:10:22.916 --> 00:10:25.083
But we are the frogs, right?

00:10:26.708 --> 00:10:27.791
Yeah.

00:10:27.875 --> 00:10:28.875
Do you remember

00:10:29.708 --> 00:10:30.916
Nicho's first birthday?

00:10:32.250 --> 00:10:33.166
What did we do?

00:10:34.416 --> 00:10:35.375
Became tadpoles.

00:10:36.041 --> 00:10:36.958
And this year?

00:10:37.833 --> 00:10:38.708
Frogs.

00:10:39.250 --> 00:10:41.291
So what does that mean?
Metamorphosis?

00:10:47.875 --> 00:10:51.833
Honey, please.

00:10:53.541 --> 00:10:55.458
Let's just buy a house.

00:10:56.541 --> 00:10:58.250
You know

00:10:58.333 --> 00:11:01.333
I made three million for each episode.

00:11:02.500 --> 00:11:04.750
In a month I can earn 90 million.

00:11:05.458 --> 00:11:08.416
My savings are enough to buy us a house.

00:11:09.250 --> 00:11:10.125
Please, honey.

00:11:15.833 --> 00:11:16.833
Dear…

00:11:20.333 --> 00:11:21.666
Be patient.

00:11:23.875 --> 00:11:26.833
You knew it from the beginning.

00:11:27.833 --> 00:11:30.125
We can't leave this house.

00:11:31.083 --> 00:11:32.958
I inherited it from my father.

00:11:34.916 --> 00:11:36.625
And what about my Mom?

00:11:36.708 --> 00:11:38.541
If we leave, she'll be all alone.

00:11:47.083 --> 00:11:49.291
Do I look impatient to you?

00:11:52.416 --> 00:11:55.041
Every day, it's always the same problem
all over again.

00:11:57.000 --> 00:11:59.000
I'm not a good daughter-in-law,

00:12:00.541 --> 00:12:05.041
not a good wife for you,
not even a good mother for Nicho.

00:12:06.083 --> 00:12:10.458
I can't cook, I woke up late,
I can't take care of my son's meals.

00:12:12.458 --> 00:12:14.041
I'm so tired.

00:12:16.250 --> 00:12:18.708
We have to follow your mother's ways.

00:12:21.041 --> 00:12:23.750
I'm a bad daughter-in-law to her.

00:12:27.458 --> 00:12:28.416
Dear.

00:12:29.625 --> 00:12:30.625
For me,

00:12:32.583 --> 00:12:37.416
you are the best wife and the best mother.

00:12:40.416 --> 00:12:41.541
Please, be patient.

00:12:43.833 --> 00:12:45.208
Take a rest, dear.

00:12:46.750 --> 00:12:47.875
Calm yourself down.

00:12:49.291 --> 00:12:51.333
Where is Nicho?

00:12:52.208 --> 00:12:55.458
I can't find him. It's too hot now.

00:12:57.375 --> 00:13:00.750
Maria Marcedes, my dear flower.

00:13:00.833 --> 00:13:03.291
Have you seen Nicho?

00:13:04.375 --> 00:13:08.208
You too, you are no less beautiful.
Even with your yellow color,

00:13:08.291 --> 00:13:10.708
but I like you, Penelope.

00:13:10.791 --> 00:13:15.791
You are so beautiful, but have you seen
my grandson here?

00:13:15.875 --> 00:13:16.833
Have you?

00:13:19.875 --> 00:13:21.625
My dear Rosalinda,

00:13:21.708 --> 00:13:25.166
a more beautiful name
than the others, but I love you all.

00:13:25.250 --> 00:13:27.375
Have you seen Nicho?

00:13:27.916 --> 00:13:30.500
Look at her.

00:13:30.583 --> 00:13:33.708
I've told her to get treatment,
but she doesn't want to.

00:13:33.791 --> 00:13:36.916
It's impossible for her to get treatment.
She's crazy, you know.

00:13:37.500 --> 00:13:39.541
You're the biggest one here, right?

00:13:39.625 --> 00:13:41.375
Have you seen Nicho?

00:13:41.458 --> 00:13:43.583
-Frog, have you seen Nicho?
-Poor her.

00:13:43.666 --> 00:13:45.625
Yeah, poor frog.

00:13:45.708 --> 00:13:47.166
Why the frog?

00:13:47.250 --> 00:13:48.541
She is.

00:13:48.625 --> 00:13:51.041
The frog's calm.
Suddenly, she's talking to it.

00:13:51.125 --> 00:13:52.625
-She's the pitiful one.
-Hey!

00:13:52.708 --> 00:13:53.625
Yes, Auntie.

00:13:53.708 --> 00:13:55.708
You guys are so busy chatting away.

00:13:55.791 --> 00:13:56.958
Where's Nicho?

00:13:57.041 --> 00:13:57.916
Have you seen him?

00:13:58.000 --> 00:13:59.250
No, I haven't.

00:13:59.333 --> 00:14:01.833
What are you doing there then?

00:14:01.916 --> 00:14:02.958
We are working.

00:14:03.041 --> 00:14:04.125
Look for him then!

00:14:04.208 --> 00:14:05.375
Do we have to?

00:14:05.458 --> 00:14:08.333
-Find him. You'd better not fail me.
-Okay.

00:14:08.416 --> 00:14:10.041
-Or I'll break your legs.
-Gosh!

00:14:10.708 --> 00:14:14.166
-Don't dawdle like a bride and groom!
-Well, we're husband and wife.

00:14:14.875 --> 00:14:17.500
You two are no bride and groom.
You guys fight nonstop.

00:14:17.583 --> 00:14:20.291
And you. You look out of shape.
Go find him!

00:14:20.375 --> 00:14:22.208
-Yes, Aunty.
-You're too slow.

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:25.083
-Hurry up!
-Yes.

00:14:25.166 --> 00:14:30.166
Find him.
Or I'll send you back to Bukit Barisan.

00:14:30.250 --> 00:14:31.583
What a cruel person.

00:14:31.666 --> 00:14:32.791
Shut up!

00:14:34.125 --> 00:14:34.958
Go on, then.

00:14:35.041 --> 00:14:38.666
-Nicho! Let's find him. Nicho!
-Nicho, where are you?

00:14:38.750 --> 00:14:39.583
Are you here?

00:14:39.666 --> 00:14:40.500
Or here maybe?

00:14:40.583 --> 00:14:42.500
-Nicho!
-Are you hiding behind the frog?

00:14:43.958 --> 00:14:44.791
Come here.

00:14:45.625 --> 00:14:49.791
-I'm so tired of looking for Nicho.
-My goodness, madame.

00:14:49.875 --> 00:14:51.000
Easy there.

00:14:51.083 --> 00:14:52.875
Here you go.

00:14:53.458 --> 00:14:55.541
Here, let's fuel up first.

00:14:55.625 --> 00:14:58.208
What! Did you just give me fuel?

00:14:58.291 --> 00:15:00.041
Do you want to burn my face?

00:15:00.125 --> 00:15:04.416
This is water from seven mountain springs.

00:15:04.500 --> 00:15:06.625
Who do you think you are?

00:15:06.708 --> 00:15:08.416
A power generator?

00:15:08.500 --> 00:15:12.958
You should've said that was the water
from those seven mountains.

00:15:13.041 --> 00:15:16.916
-Be polite to me!
-So unclear, I still have work to do.

00:15:17.625 --> 00:15:19.791
Sis, you're so naive.

00:15:20.333 --> 00:15:24.916
That's what happens when you
just play around, dance, and shop.

00:15:25.000 --> 00:15:26.750
You've got nothing in your head.

00:15:26.833 --> 00:15:27.958
Look at me.

00:15:28.041 --> 00:15:30.208
I read two books a week.

00:15:30.291 --> 00:15:33.041
What have you got from that?

00:15:33.125 --> 00:15:35.583
You're single.
How dare you give me advice?

00:15:36.375 --> 00:15:41.250
You don't have a husband either.
He's no longer here.

00:15:41.333 --> 00:15:45.125
I just haven't met anyone on my level yet.

00:15:45.208 --> 00:15:49.000
When I meet him, he'll be my husband.

00:15:49.833 --> 00:15:51.750
-You talk a lot.
-So what?

00:15:51.833 --> 00:15:54.916
-Should I inject your tongue?
-Oh, you're just distracting me.

00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:57.416
Take off your glasses,
so you can see my face.

00:15:57.500 --> 00:15:59.000
Mom, stop it!

00:15:59.083 --> 00:16:02.208
Think first before you speak.
You just say whatever you want.

00:16:02.291 --> 00:16:03.583
Hey, Mom, it's time to eat.

00:16:03.666 --> 00:16:07.208
-You live under my roof!
-My dearest Mom, that's enough. Come on.

00:16:07.708 --> 00:16:08.541
Stupid.

00:16:08.625 --> 00:16:10.708
-You stupid one.
-You're the stupidest.

00:16:10.791 --> 00:16:14.416
Stop saying that or I'll punch you.

00:16:14.500 --> 00:16:16.000
Let's have a breakfast.

00:16:16.083 --> 00:16:18.416
-Stop it! I'm hungry. Just eat.
-It's her!

00:16:18.500 --> 00:16:20.500
Stop acting like a child.

00:16:20.583 --> 00:16:22.500
She doesn't respect me at all.

00:16:22.583 --> 00:16:23.708
Stop it.

00:16:23.791 --> 00:16:24.666
Let's eat first.

00:16:24.750 --> 00:16:25.916
My cooking's good, huh?

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:26.916
Awesome.

00:16:27.000 --> 00:16:29.750
-Get some of those.
-Of course.

00:16:31.750 --> 00:16:32.708
Move your glass.

00:16:33.916 --> 00:16:36.666
-What do you want, Mom?
-Let me get it myself.

00:16:38.833 --> 00:16:43.083
Hey, where's your wife?

00:16:43.875 --> 00:16:44.875
Still working.

00:16:44.958 --> 00:16:46.125
She's busy.

00:16:47.375 --> 00:16:48.875
She's always working.

00:16:48.958 --> 00:16:50.166
What's this?

00:16:50.250 --> 00:16:52.916
We're all supposed to eat here together.

00:16:54.125 --> 00:16:56.000
Why don't you get some rest?

00:16:56.083 --> 00:16:59.291
Yes, but I want to see Nicho first.

00:16:59.375 --> 00:17:00.625
Where is he?

00:17:00.708 --> 00:17:01.541
Hey!

00:17:02.500 --> 00:17:06.083
Cook something for your husband.

00:17:06.166 --> 00:17:08.416
Look at him.

00:17:08.500 --> 00:17:09.833
He's starving.

00:17:09.916 --> 00:17:10.916
That's my cooking.

00:17:11.458 --> 00:17:12.666
Mom, it's still early.

00:17:12.750 --> 00:17:14.291
You never cook.

00:17:14.375 --> 00:17:16.583
He eats whatever I put on this table.

00:17:18.041 --> 00:17:21.041
Mom, you know I have a lot of work to do.

00:17:21.875 --> 00:17:26.000
And if he wants to eat,
we can order food online.

00:17:26.083 --> 00:17:28.666
Listen to you, so full of wisdom.

00:17:29.166 --> 00:17:31.583
Ordering food online?

00:17:32.166 --> 00:17:35.916
He wants a home-cooked meal
from his own wife! That is our tradition.

00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:37.208
Enough, Mom.

00:17:38.166 --> 00:17:41.541
She's busy.
Just eat or you'll get sick.

00:17:41.625 --> 00:17:44.708
Raja, you also work.

00:17:44.791 --> 00:17:46.916
But you can manage your time.

00:17:47.000 --> 00:17:48.666
And here she is.

00:17:48.750 --> 00:17:50.208
Come on.

00:17:50.291 --> 00:17:51.833
Let's eat first.

00:17:52.541 --> 00:17:53.375
Dig in.

00:17:57.041 --> 00:17:58.458
It's delicious, right?

00:18:00.041 --> 00:18:01.833
You can't even cook like this.

00:18:02.458 --> 00:18:03.625
All you do is work.

00:18:03.708 --> 00:18:05.041
So busy.

00:18:07.708 --> 00:18:08.583
Seriously!

00:18:08.666 --> 00:18:10.125
Mom, please don't.

00:18:10.208 --> 00:18:11.208
Enough!

00:18:11.291 --> 00:18:12.375
That's my job, Mom.

00:18:12.458 --> 00:18:13.416
I have a deadline.

00:18:13.500 --> 00:18:14.750
This is my house!

00:18:14.833 --> 00:18:20.208
You can't use your phone while eating.
That's our tradition.

00:18:20.291 --> 00:18:22.125
These are the rules of my house.

00:18:22.208 --> 00:18:25.000
No matter what,
you have to follow the rules.

00:18:25.083 --> 00:18:26.375
Understand?

00:18:26.458 --> 00:18:27.333
Yes, Mom.

00:18:27.416 --> 00:18:29.708
-Don't make me repeat myself!
-Yes, Mom.

00:18:29.791 --> 00:18:31.000
You're stressing me out!

00:18:32.083 --> 00:18:33.666
Grandma!

00:18:33.750 --> 00:18:37.583
My dear grandson, where have you been?

00:18:37.666 --> 00:18:39.041
Why are you so wet?

00:18:39.125 --> 00:18:40.875
Who threw you in?

00:18:40.958 --> 00:18:44.666
It was him who threw me in.

00:18:45.791 --> 00:18:46.666
How dare you?

00:18:46.750 --> 00:18:48.000
He jumped on his own.

00:18:48.083 --> 00:18:50.083
There's no way he's lying!

00:18:50.166 --> 00:18:51.416
Don't lie.

00:18:51.500 --> 00:18:54.041
No more of your deceit here.

00:18:54.125 --> 00:18:56.458
-Right.
-You're messing around.

00:18:56.541 --> 00:18:58.041
Let's clean yourself up.

00:18:58.583 --> 00:19:00.458
Hey, listen.

00:19:00.541 --> 00:19:03.125
-This floor is dirty.
-Yes, we know.

00:19:03.208 --> 00:19:05.500
If you don't clean it, it'll get slippery.

00:19:05.583 --> 00:19:08.833
My grandson might fall on it
and I'll finish you.

00:19:08.916 --> 00:19:10.583
-I'll end you!
-Okay, we'll do it.

00:19:10.666 --> 00:19:11.791
-Go away.
-Yes, Auntie.

00:19:11.875 --> 00:19:13.000
Let's take a shower.

00:19:13.666 --> 00:19:15.041
Honey, let's hit the shower.

00:19:15.125 --> 00:19:16.083
What are you saying?

00:19:16.166 --> 00:19:17.458
All right, let's go.

00:19:18.541 --> 00:19:19.916
Excuse us.

00:19:22.333 --> 00:19:23.250
I'm going, Mom.

00:19:24.375 --> 00:19:25.791
Let's go. Hey!

00:19:26.583 --> 00:19:27.916
Why did you run away?

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:30.791
There must be someone waiting.

00:19:30.875 --> 00:19:33.708
You're just like your father,
so handsome.

00:19:34.208 --> 00:19:36.166
You have to say goodbye to me first.

00:19:37.208 --> 00:19:40.291
-Study hard. Don't be naughty.
-Yes, Grandma. Bye!

00:19:40.375 --> 00:19:42.000
All right. Bye, Grandma!

00:19:42.958 --> 00:19:46.833
Your wife should've taken him to school,
not you.

00:19:48.083 --> 00:19:49.208
Come on, Mom.

00:19:49.291 --> 00:19:50.416
She's busy.

00:19:50.500 --> 00:19:53.083
Go easy on her. Stop pushing her, okay?

00:19:53.166 --> 00:19:54.000
What does she do?

00:19:54.500 --> 00:19:57.291
Staying in her room 24 hours,
like a bride to be.

00:19:57.375 --> 00:19:58.583
Seeing her upsets me.

00:19:59.708 --> 00:20:00.541
Enough, Mom.

00:20:02.333 --> 00:20:03.875
I have to go.

00:20:04.541 --> 00:20:07.583
-All right then. Be careful.
-Sure.

00:20:09.625 --> 00:20:15.000
Don't forget, today my friends and I
will be practicing dance here.

00:20:15.083 --> 00:20:16.375
Find another place.

00:20:16.458 --> 00:20:17.583
Why?

00:20:18.208 --> 00:20:21.333
You know I don't like your friends.

00:20:21.416 --> 00:20:22.791
They're all consumptive.

00:20:23.375 --> 00:20:24.250
I need to go.

00:20:24.333 --> 00:20:25.166
Whatever.

00:20:27.125 --> 00:20:29.041
What is he saying, that "consump-tive"?

00:20:29.625 --> 00:20:32.041
It's so hard
to understand kids these days.

00:20:34.708 --> 00:20:35.833
Oh, wait!

00:20:38.291 --> 00:20:39.625
You scared me, Mom!

00:20:39.708 --> 00:20:42.625
Raja, do you have money to buy me a piano?

00:20:42.708 --> 00:20:45.333
My friend bought a piano yesterday.

00:20:45.416 --> 00:20:47.166
I want it too.

00:20:47.875 --> 00:20:49.375
Mom, please.

00:20:49.458 --> 00:20:51.541
You can't even play the piano.

00:20:51.625 --> 00:20:53.583
Don't be jealous of your friends.

00:20:54.375 --> 00:20:56.083
You think I can't play the piano?

00:20:56.958 --> 00:20:59.708
I can cook, sing, anything.

00:20:59.791 --> 00:21:01.958
-I can even do somersaults. Want to see?
-No!

00:21:02.041 --> 00:21:04.125
No, Mom. No need, Mom.

00:21:04.208 --> 00:21:07.208
I don't have the money
like father used to give you.

00:21:07.291 --> 00:21:08.958
Mom, you don't even need it.

00:21:09.041 --> 00:21:10.583
Why are you like this?

00:21:11.166 --> 00:21:14.208
You asked for a crocodile leather bag
the other day as well.

00:21:14.291 --> 00:21:16.916
Why are talking about crocodiles now?

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:18.750
You always jealous of your friends.

00:21:18.833 --> 00:21:20.708
Enough. It's dangerous.

00:21:20.791 --> 00:21:21.625
Fine.

00:21:22.208 --> 00:21:23.833
-I'm late, Mom.
-Then go.

00:21:24.666 --> 00:21:25.916
You're stingy.

00:21:43.291 --> 00:21:48.291
Aren't you annoyed by your mother-in-law?

00:21:48.833 --> 00:21:52.208
She wants to manage everything.

00:21:52.291 --> 00:21:55.083
I'd have been gone by now if I were you.

00:21:55.916 --> 00:22:02.916
That's exactly what I want, Auntie.

00:22:03.583 --> 00:22:06.750
But will she ever let her son to do that?

00:22:07.708 --> 00:22:08.708
Come on!

00:22:09.541 --> 00:22:13.458
If I were you, I'd be so mad.

00:22:13.541 --> 00:22:15.625
If it weren't because of Raja,

00:22:15.708 --> 00:22:17.833
I'd have already left this house.

00:22:18.916 --> 00:22:22.958
But it seems like you're only allowed
to leave once you get married.

00:22:24.375 --> 00:22:26.375
If not, it's impossible.

00:22:26.458 --> 00:22:28.375
I don't know.

00:22:28.458 --> 00:22:32.750
I want to be married.

00:22:33.333 --> 00:22:36.000
But God hasn't sent me my soulmate yet.

00:22:36.083 --> 00:22:41.250
But if you and Raja were to leave,
could I come with you?

00:22:43.708 --> 00:22:45.458
Go where?

00:22:46.458 --> 00:22:48.666
There's Nicho and Raja.

00:22:48.750 --> 00:22:51.625
How can we possibly leave this house?

00:22:51.708 --> 00:22:53.625
That's her happiness.

00:22:54.208 --> 00:22:56.291
Don't be so obedient.

00:22:56.375 --> 00:22:58.250
How dare he?

00:22:59.250 --> 00:23:03.125
I only asked for a piano, not a mountain.

00:23:05.416 --> 00:23:08.041
My friends always get what they want.

00:23:09.000 --> 00:23:10.916
You want to buy a piano?

00:23:13.458 --> 00:23:14.708
No, I don't need it.

00:23:14.791 --> 00:23:15.750
It's okay, Mom.

00:23:15.833 --> 00:23:17.125
Let me buy it for you.

00:23:17.875 --> 00:23:19.916
-Are you serious?
-Of course.

00:23:20.000 --> 00:23:22.125
You don't have to do that.

00:23:22.208 --> 00:23:24.708
Don't worry.

00:23:26.291 --> 00:23:27.291
All right, then.

00:23:27.833 --> 00:23:29.750
-It's 50 million, anyway.
-Correct, Mom.

00:23:33.458 --> 00:23:34.583
What is this?

00:23:35.541 --> 00:23:37.041
You can't even make a coffee?

00:23:37.583 --> 00:23:39.083
Let me teach you, okay?

00:23:39.750 --> 00:23:41.166
Yes, Mom.

00:23:45.000 --> 00:23:48.875
You're like a cash machine to her.

00:23:49.666 --> 00:23:51.125
Stop staying yes.

00:23:51.208 --> 00:23:52.583
She didn't even say thanks.

00:23:54.500 --> 00:23:55.916
It's fine, Auntie.

00:23:56.541 --> 00:23:58.166
As long as she's happy.

00:23:59.875 --> 00:24:03.333
Tie and chair. Tie…

00:24:09.583 --> 00:24:10.916
What does that mean?

00:24:11.000 --> 00:24:12.250
I think the app's broken.

00:24:12.916 --> 00:24:14.708
-Stupid app.
-Sir.

00:24:14.791 --> 00:24:16.500
What trash.

00:24:17.041 --> 00:24:17.958
Sir!

00:24:18.875 --> 00:24:20.791
-What is it, Sum?
-Do you even have ears?

00:24:21.958 --> 00:24:24.041
-What?
-You're too straight-forward, Sum.

00:24:24.541 --> 00:24:25.458
Oh, my goodness.

00:24:25.541 --> 00:24:27.666
I know I'm sweet, but not like this.

00:24:27.750 --> 00:24:29.791
Oh, please.
You smell like a wet towel.

00:24:29.875 --> 00:24:30.958
Not my favorite.

00:24:31.041 --> 00:24:33.666
-Let me tell you something.
-A wet towel?

00:24:34.458 --> 00:24:38.708
-What's that called?
-Hey!

00:24:38.791 --> 00:24:40.333
-How dare you?
-You're dead.

00:24:40.916 --> 00:24:42.291
She tried to kiss me.

00:24:43.500 --> 00:24:47.875
If I were a homewrecker, I'd be picky,
I'd choose the neighbor, he's rich.

00:24:47.958 --> 00:24:49.958
Just say you want my husband.

00:24:51.250 --> 00:24:52.750
I have some news.

00:24:52.833 --> 00:24:53.666
What news?

00:24:53.750 --> 00:24:59.416
In this house, there's a bomb
that's about to explode.

00:24:59.500 --> 00:25:00.750
-Bomb?
-Bomb?

00:25:00.833 --> 00:25:02.250
So that bomb…

00:25:02.333 --> 00:25:03.541
Honey!

00:25:03.625 --> 00:25:06.333
Why didn't you take me?
It's a bomb, honey!

00:25:06.416 --> 00:25:07.916
Yeah, it's about to explode!

00:25:08.000 --> 00:25:09.208
Hey, what's wrong?

00:25:09.291 --> 00:25:10.125
Hey!

00:25:11.208 --> 00:25:16.000
Hey! I wanted to tell some hot news.
Why did you run away? Whatever.

00:25:17.250 --> 00:25:19.375
What else do you want me
to change, sir?

00:25:19.458 --> 00:25:21.583
So I can revise it at once.

00:25:21.666 --> 00:25:27.250
Oh, gosh. That scene where the police
are chasing them.

00:25:27.333 --> 00:25:31.125
Why do you have to make them
jump into the lake? Huh?

00:25:31.625 --> 00:25:34.041
You know, the lake is dangerous.

00:25:34.125 --> 00:25:36.166
Tons of poisonous snakes in there.

00:25:36.250 --> 00:25:38.208
Don't put my actors through that!

00:25:38.291 --> 00:25:42.791
-Daddy…
-Bye, Daddy.

00:25:44.291 --> 00:25:46.958
-I'll call you later, okay?
-Okay, see you.

00:25:47.666 --> 00:25:49.083
-Bye Daddy.
-Bye.

00:25:50.958 --> 00:25:52.541
Did you hear that?

00:25:53.166 --> 00:25:54.708
They called me Daddy.

00:25:55.333 --> 00:25:57.791
I'm like a parent to them.

00:25:57.875 --> 00:25:59.666
So, if anything happens to them…

00:25:59.750 --> 00:26:02.750
I'm the one who has
to cover the hospital costs.

00:26:02.833 --> 00:26:05.708
I'm going to lose so much! Come on.

00:26:05.791 --> 00:26:07.041
I see.

00:26:08.916 --> 00:26:11.000
Then I'll just make them fall and roll.

00:26:11.083 --> 00:26:12.416
And they get caught.

00:26:12.500 --> 00:26:15.083
Whatever. Change it to whatever you want.

00:26:15.166 --> 00:26:17.833
Just don't make them
jump into the lake, okay?

00:26:17.916 --> 00:26:20.583
You scratch my back,
and I'll scratch yours.

00:26:21.875 --> 00:26:23.083
Just don't be late.

00:26:23.166 --> 00:26:25.750
Yes, I'll send you
the revision straight away, sir.

00:26:27.750 --> 00:26:29.458
Yes, immediately, sir.

00:26:31.833 --> 00:26:34.125
Hey, did you hear that?

00:26:34.208 --> 00:26:35.166
Was it good?

00:26:35.250 --> 00:26:36.500
Very good, sir.

00:26:37.708 --> 00:26:39.875
What did I say?
What's good?

00:26:40.583 --> 00:26:41.833
All you do is eat.

00:27:37.791 --> 00:27:39.000
My son.

00:27:41.083 --> 00:27:42.208
Raja, come here.

00:27:42.291 --> 00:27:44.000
This is my handsome son, Raja.

00:27:44.083 --> 00:27:46.500
-Hey, Raja.
-Hi, Raja.

00:27:46.583 --> 00:27:47.583
Hi, Raja.

00:27:48.625 --> 00:27:49.541
What is it, Mom?

00:27:50.083 --> 00:27:51.958
I'm so happy today.

00:27:52.458 --> 00:27:54.000
These people are my friends.

00:27:54.541 --> 00:27:56.291
We're practicing for my birthday.

00:27:57.583 --> 00:27:59.083
Can't you find another place?

00:28:00.000 --> 00:28:00.958
Come here.

00:28:01.041 --> 00:28:03.750
The one with long hair and wearing gold.

00:28:03.833 --> 00:28:05.416
She just had facial surgery.

00:28:06.125 --> 00:28:08.208
I want to have a face like that.

00:28:08.291 --> 00:28:10.166
So, I can look like her.

00:28:10.250 --> 00:28:12.791
-You're jealous?
-She's beautiful and I'm ugly.

00:28:12.875 --> 00:28:14.666
Mom, come on. Why are you like this?

00:28:15.583 --> 00:28:17.750
You are already beautiful.
Stop it, Mom.

00:28:17.833 --> 00:28:20.416
That's why Dad like
and fell in love with you.

00:28:20.500 --> 00:28:21.791
Come on.

00:28:21.875 --> 00:28:23.375
You are indeed stingy.

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:25.375
I don't have the money, Mom.

00:28:28.875 --> 00:28:31.375
My son said I'm still beautiful.

00:28:35.000 --> 00:28:38.083
But I'm turning 50 soon.

00:28:38.166 --> 00:28:41.333
-Are you for real?
-I don't believe it.

00:28:41.416 --> 00:28:43.875
You're still young and beautiful.

00:28:43.958 --> 00:28:45.125
What do you think?

00:28:46.375 --> 00:28:48.250
Hey, want to look as good as me?

00:28:48.333 --> 00:28:50.166
Go to Korea for surgery!

00:28:50.875 --> 00:28:53.291
So we'll look like 25 years old.

00:28:53.375 --> 00:28:55.791
But if it's still like this,
it's not healed yet.

00:28:56.833 --> 00:28:58.500
Fresh out of surgery.

00:28:59.166 --> 00:29:01.708
If you want to look young,
you have to be like me.

00:29:02.666 --> 00:29:04.208
-All right.
-Let's dance again.

00:29:04.291 --> 00:29:06.625
-Let's practice one more time!
-Let's do it.

00:29:31.208 --> 00:29:32.625
Dear.

00:29:33.791 --> 00:29:36.125
Mom is so noisy.

00:29:37.833 --> 00:29:39.708
I can't concentrate.

00:29:40.291 --> 00:29:42.208
But you bought her a piano.

00:29:43.500 --> 00:29:45.041
Then what can I do?

00:29:46.750 --> 00:29:48.208
Why did you buy it?

00:29:49.208 --> 00:29:50.291
I'm sorry, dear.

00:29:50.791 --> 00:29:52.750
She demanded a lot from you.

00:29:53.458 --> 00:29:54.666
She has a lot of money.

00:29:55.458 --> 00:29:56.958
I gave all my money to her.

00:29:59.583 --> 00:30:01.750
I'm sick of all her friends.

00:30:02.333 --> 00:30:04.375
Dancing around like that.

00:30:05.166 --> 00:30:07.125
Just let them be. Be patient.

00:30:08.166 --> 00:30:10.041
Her happiness is all that matters.

00:30:38.958 --> 00:30:40.125
What is this?

00:30:48.125 --> 00:30:49.916
I don't see anyone around.

00:30:54.916 --> 00:30:57.333
Are they crazy?

00:30:58.458 --> 00:31:00.458
They don't even know it's my birthday.

00:31:02.541 --> 00:31:04.708
Honey, can you hear my voice?

00:31:07.166 --> 00:31:09.291
This house is so quiet, like a graveyard.

00:31:09.375 --> 00:31:10.208
Honey…

00:31:12.500 --> 00:31:13.708
No "happy birthday."

00:31:13.791 --> 00:31:15.125
What is this?

00:31:15.833 --> 00:31:16.958
Don't just stare at me!

00:31:19.666 --> 00:31:21.000
You're such a crybaby.

00:31:21.916 --> 00:31:23.458
Your face is so ugly.

00:31:24.666 --> 00:31:26.791
Go wipe it with a handkerchief.

00:31:34.500 --> 00:31:37.125
My heart aches, my beloved flowers.

00:31:37.791 --> 00:31:39.583
No one remembered my birthday today.

00:31:40.333 --> 00:31:43.875
My fish, may you always be
happy together.

00:31:43.958 --> 00:31:45.500
And me…

00:31:45.583 --> 00:31:47.166
No one remembers my birthday.

00:31:48.666 --> 00:31:50.041
I'm so sad.

00:31:55.958 --> 00:31:58.541
Happy birthday to you

00:31:59.625 --> 00:32:02.541
Happy birthday to you

00:32:03.416 --> 00:32:07.166
Happy birthday, happy birthday

00:32:07.250 --> 00:32:09.833
Happy birthday to you

00:32:11.250 --> 00:32:14.125
I thought you guys forgot my birthday.

00:32:14.208 --> 00:32:15.291
How can we?

00:32:15.375 --> 00:32:17.125
Maybe I'll be in nursing home soon.

00:32:17.208 --> 00:32:19.666
How could we forget?

00:32:19.750 --> 00:32:22.416
-Blow out the candles, Mom.
-Let's blow out the candles.

00:32:26.166 --> 00:32:28.166
Happy birthday, Mom.

00:32:29.041 --> 00:32:31.000
Happy birthday, sis.

00:32:32.750 --> 00:32:34.166
Let's take a picture.

00:32:45.458 --> 00:32:47.166
Hello, sir.

00:32:49.458 --> 00:32:51.458
Yes. How is it going? All right.

00:32:51.541 --> 00:32:53.708
Smile! Show your yellow teeth.

00:32:56.791 --> 00:32:57.625
More.

00:32:58.666 --> 00:33:01.708
-What should I wear tonight?
-Hi, Mom.

00:33:01.791 --> 00:33:03.958
Hey, where have you been?

00:33:05.833 --> 00:33:07.291
Why are you smiling?

00:33:07.375 --> 00:33:09.791
-What kind of present do you want?
-My dear son.

00:33:11.166 --> 00:33:12.166
Sit down first.

00:33:12.916 --> 00:33:14.750
I don't need birthday presents.

00:33:15.875 --> 00:33:17.250
Are you sure?

00:33:17.333 --> 00:33:19.375
As long as you're here, I'm good.

00:33:20.166 --> 00:33:22.125
The important thing is
stay with me, okay?

00:33:22.208 --> 00:33:24.083
-I'm getting old, you know.
-I know.

00:33:26.000 --> 00:33:28.958
-And don't forget…
-What is it?

00:33:29.041 --> 00:33:33.083
I want to celebrate my birthday here,
tonight.

00:33:33.166 --> 00:33:35.416
With all my friends,
also my other old friends.

00:33:36.541 --> 00:33:37.875
Why the long face?

00:33:37.958 --> 00:33:39.125
It's okay, right?

00:33:39.208 --> 00:33:40.250
Come on, Mom.

00:33:41.416 --> 00:33:43.458
Let's just celebrate with family.

00:33:43.541 --> 00:33:46.083
Which restaurant? Just name it.

00:33:46.166 --> 00:33:47.416
But just us.

00:33:48.958 --> 00:33:52.416
You don't understand your mother well.

00:33:53.208 --> 00:33:55.166
Your mom is different from your wife.

00:33:56.083 --> 00:33:59.291
She just stays at home, like a laying hen.

00:33:59.958 --> 00:34:01.500
I've never seen her going out.

00:34:02.875 --> 00:34:05.083
Please understand me.

00:34:05.791 --> 00:34:07.041
You know she's working.

00:34:07.125 --> 00:34:08.208
Whatever you say.

00:34:09.208 --> 00:34:11.500
I've got a headache.

00:34:13.208 --> 00:34:14.458
Leave Andara out of this.

00:34:15.000 --> 00:34:16.208
Going somewhere?

00:34:16.291 --> 00:34:19.291
-It's cold.
-Don't forget to buy me a sponge cake.

00:34:19.833 --> 00:34:20.833
Delicious and big.

00:34:21.375 --> 00:34:23.416
As big as Lake Toba and Samosir Island.

00:34:23.958 --> 00:34:25.208
Don't forget, okay?

00:34:25.291 --> 00:34:27.625
I'll get you as big as
the island of Kalimantan?

00:34:28.625 --> 00:34:30.375
My dear son.

00:34:30.458 --> 00:34:32.041
He's always joking around.

00:34:40.916 --> 00:34:41.875
Donda!

00:34:55.833 --> 00:34:57.041
We love you!

00:35:04.041 --> 00:35:06.666
-Let me take it off. Be patient.
-Hurry up!

00:35:08.208 --> 00:35:09.208
Happy birthday!

00:35:09.291 --> 00:35:11.250
Happy birthday, darling.

00:35:13.833 --> 00:35:15.125
Okay, Donda, Donda.

00:35:17.250 --> 00:35:18.583
What is it?

00:35:20.500 --> 00:35:21.375
Okay.

00:35:23.875 --> 00:35:25.833
These shoes are not comfortable.

00:35:28.125 --> 00:35:29.416
Look at your auntie.

00:35:31.375 --> 00:35:32.916
-Okay.
-Turn slowly.

00:35:33.416 --> 00:35:35.333
It's so heavy too. What's in it?

00:35:35.875 --> 00:35:37.916
I have no idea, it's heavy.

00:35:39.125 --> 00:35:43.125
On the count of three,
open your eyes, okay Donda?

00:35:43.208 --> 00:35:45.000
Are you ready?

00:35:45.083 --> 00:35:47.416
One, two…

00:35:47.500 --> 00:35:49.583
Three.

00:35:56.208 --> 00:35:57.416
What is this?

00:35:57.500 --> 00:35:59.125
What is this? I'm scared.

00:35:59.916 --> 00:36:01.250
Oh, my goodness gracious.

00:36:01.333 --> 00:36:03.041
Apparently this is a living doll.

00:36:47.666 --> 00:36:48.791
Hello, sir?

00:36:48.875 --> 00:36:51.375
Yes.
I just got home.

00:36:51.458 --> 00:36:52.541
Let's go, Nicho.

00:36:54.166 --> 00:36:56.500
Yes, sir.
I'll send it straight away.

00:37:01.666 --> 00:37:03.625
Mom, I need to pee.

00:37:03.708 --> 00:37:05.583
Yes, dear. Let's go.

00:37:05.666 --> 00:37:07.250
And then we go to sleep, okay?

00:37:07.750 --> 00:37:09.291
This event is for adults.

00:37:09.875 --> 00:37:12.291
-Hurry up, Mom. Can't hold it anymore.
-All right.

00:37:51.000 --> 00:37:51.833
Mom!

00:38:12.500 --> 00:38:13.875
What the hell is this?

00:38:15.041 --> 00:38:19.708
How did my mother's birthday party
turn into such a tacky affair?

00:38:20.708 --> 00:38:21.541
Why?

00:38:22.208 --> 00:38:23.916
You don't need to shout like that.

00:38:24.916 --> 00:38:26.625
This is just for fun.

00:38:27.458 --> 00:38:28.625
Just for fun?

00:38:29.583 --> 00:38:32.458
Don't forget that
you are a mother and a wife.

00:38:33.000 --> 00:38:36.291
Dad's no longer here,
but you should have some self-respect.

00:38:36.875 --> 00:38:38.666
I thought you were loyal.
But what?

00:38:40.041 --> 00:38:41.291
Watch your mouth.

00:38:42.000 --> 00:38:43.541
I'm still loyal to your father.

00:38:44.166 --> 00:38:46.375
And this is just a birthday party.

00:38:47.208 --> 00:38:50.125
This is indeed your birthday party,
but not like this.

00:38:52.500 --> 00:38:54.750
Honey, let's go.

00:38:54.833 --> 00:38:58.875
Don't embarrass your mother
in front of people like this.

00:38:59.416 --> 00:39:02.125
You're the one who threw away
your own dignity.

00:39:02.208 --> 00:39:03.333
Do you know that?

00:39:03.416 --> 00:39:04.750
Watch your mouth!

00:39:04.833 --> 00:39:06.041
I know.

00:39:06.125 --> 00:39:07.500
Because I'm defending you.

00:39:09.958 --> 00:39:14.000
For those of you
used to this kind of trash,

00:39:15.000 --> 00:39:18.208
don't you dare bring my mother into it.

00:39:18.291 --> 00:39:19.125
Got it!

00:39:19.208 --> 00:39:20.333
Honey…

00:39:21.250 --> 00:39:22.083
Honey.

00:39:24.875 --> 00:39:25.708
And you.

00:39:26.375 --> 00:39:27.458
Yes, you.

00:39:29.625 --> 00:39:32.166
Don't you have any better job than this?

00:39:32.875 --> 00:39:34.625
I'm here because I was invited.

00:39:36.333 --> 00:39:37.458
Invited?

00:39:38.333 --> 00:39:41.208
Enough, honey, let's go inside.

00:39:41.291 --> 00:39:42.166
Come on.

00:39:43.375 --> 00:39:44.458
-All right.
-This…

00:39:44.541 --> 00:39:46.041
You take care of Nicho.

00:39:46.125 --> 00:39:46.958
Go to Nicho.

00:39:48.041 --> 00:39:50.208
-Honey--
-You're invited? Okay.

00:39:53.416 --> 00:39:55.250
Even if you're invited,

00:39:55.333 --> 00:39:57.916
don't you dare lay a finger on my mother!

00:40:00.666 --> 00:40:02.916
Oh, no, please stop it!

00:40:05.833 --> 00:40:06.666
He's a guest.

00:40:09.916 --> 00:40:11.583
That's enough.

00:40:11.666 --> 00:40:12.541
-Go away!
-Raja!

00:40:13.458 --> 00:40:14.625
Raja!

00:40:14.708 --> 00:40:16.291
Enough, let's get inside, honey.

00:40:17.333 --> 00:40:18.833
Sumi.

00:40:18.916 --> 00:40:21.041
Come on, hon. Let's just go inside.

00:40:21.666 --> 00:40:24.500
If you want to indulge your cheap desires,

00:40:24.583 --> 00:40:28.750
do it away from my mother
and not here, in my father's house!

00:40:30.000 --> 00:40:31.041
Watch your mouth!

00:40:31.541 --> 00:40:33.708
You can't shout like that.

00:40:33.791 --> 00:40:35.958
You used to be a good kid.

00:40:36.041 --> 00:40:38.625
But now, you've gone bad.

00:40:38.708 --> 00:40:42.000
It's all because of your wife, right?

00:40:42.083 --> 00:40:48.333
Just because she's a screenwriter,
everything is made into a drama. Right?

00:40:48.416 --> 00:40:51.083
Ma'am, please watch your mouth.

00:40:51.583 --> 00:40:53.208
Leave my wife out of this!

00:40:54.208 --> 00:40:55.083
Enough, Raja.

00:40:55.583 --> 00:40:56.416
Enough!

00:40:57.208 --> 00:40:58.625
Your wife is shameless.

00:41:00.125 --> 00:41:01.125
Ungrateful.

00:41:01.958 --> 00:41:05.000
She can't take care of you
and always talks back to me.

00:41:06.208 --> 00:41:07.583
She took you away from me.

00:41:10.000 --> 00:41:11.708
How dare you point at me!

00:41:11.791 --> 00:41:13.166
What's wrong with you?

00:41:15.583 --> 00:41:16.625
Dear.

00:41:21.541 --> 00:41:22.750
Now open your eyes.

00:41:23.416 --> 00:41:25.791
Look at that!

00:41:25.875 --> 00:41:27.583
Your wife is full of drama,

00:41:27.666 --> 00:41:31.125
yet you dare to do that
to your own mother?

00:41:32.250 --> 00:41:34.291
And you said that this party was tacky?

00:41:35.916 --> 00:41:37.541
What kind of wife do you have?

00:41:37.625 --> 00:41:38.541
Shut up!

00:41:39.833 --> 00:41:40.708
Oh, my gosh!

00:41:40.791 --> 00:41:41.666
Donda, stop.

00:41:41.750 --> 00:41:43.041
-Calm down.
-Stay calm.

00:41:43.125 --> 00:41:44.583
-You need to stay calm.
-Sumi.

00:41:46.083 --> 00:41:48.291
-Bring her inside.
-I'm so embarrassed.

00:41:48.375 --> 00:41:49.583
-Poor Donda.
-Oh, my God.

00:41:50.458 --> 00:41:52.750
-I'm embarrassed, Sumi.
-Ma'am, this is the bill.

00:41:52.833 --> 00:41:53.833
What is this!

00:41:54.500 --> 00:41:55.416
You're crazy!

00:41:56.666 --> 00:41:59.166
-Sumi, I'm so embarrassed.
-Stay calm.

00:42:01.083 --> 00:42:02.500
Check, check.

00:42:02.583 --> 00:42:03.458
Okay!

00:42:04.333 --> 00:42:05.291
Move aside.

00:42:05.375 --> 00:42:06.250
Later.

00:42:06.333 --> 00:42:08.041
Ladies and flirty men,

00:42:08.125 --> 00:42:11.500
have a nice evening,
that was the highlight of our event.

00:42:11.583 --> 00:42:13.916
Great, right?
Give a round of applause.

00:42:14.791 --> 00:42:16.875
That was character development.

00:42:17.458 --> 00:42:18.708
Just acting.

00:42:18.791 --> 00:42:21.875
It's all over now.
You can go home in peace.

00:42:22.500 --> 00:42:25.000
Don't leave anything behind.
Please go home.

00:42:26.083 --> 00:42:26.916
Hurry up.

00:42:27.666 --> 00:42:28.791
Take care.

00:42:28.875 --> 00:42:30.250
-Okay, bye.
-Let's go home.

00:42:30.333 --> 00:42:31.875
We can't stay here. Let's go.

00:42:31.958 --> 00:42:32.916
-I'm off then.
-Sure.

00:42:33.000 --> 00:42:34.458
-All good?
-Yes.

00:42:34.541 --> 00:42:35.416
Thank you.

00:42:40.916 --> 00:42:42.250
Pick me up, honey!

00:42:44.250 --> 00:42:45.791
It's our son.

00:42:45.875 --> 00:42:47.666
Take me with you!

00:42:47.750 --> 00:42:48.916
I just want to die!

00:42:49.541 --> 00:42:50.791
You see that?

00:42:50.875 --> 00:42:52.958
He humiliated me.

00:42:53.041 --> 00:42:54.500
I want to die!

00:42:54.583 --> 00:42:55.958
Take me with you!

00:42:57.041 --> 00:42:59.166
-Did she mention ending it all?
-We'll see.

00:42:59.666 --> 00:43:01.375
-Report this.
-Okay.

00:43:01.458 --> 00:43:02.583
Take me with you.

00:43:04.041 --> 00:43:04.958
To whom?

00:43:05.041 --> 00:43:06.208
To Raja, of course.

00:43:06.291 --> 00:43:09.291
I'm afraid she's going
to follow her husband for real.

00:43:09.375 --> 00:43:10.541
Where is she going?

00:43:10.625 --> 00:43:11.458
To the mall.

00:43:12.166 --> 00:43:14.000
Her husband's up there.

00:43:14.083 --> 00:43:15.000
-Heaven?
-Yes.

00:43:15.083 --> 00:43:16.375
Oh, my God. All right then.

00:43:22.375 --> 00:43:24.375
Honey, I need to go to the toilet.

00:43:24.458 --> 00:43:27.541
Just keep it in the room,
otherwise it'll jump into the toilet.

00:43:27.625 --> 00:43:29.208
-Yeah, you're right.
-Go on, then.

00:43:31.416 --> 00:43:32.750
Hey, add one more.

00:43:38.500 --> 00:43:39.708
Lord.

00:43:39.791 --> 00:43:40.708
Lord Raja.

00:43:43.625 --> 00:43:44.583
What is it?

00:43:44.666 --> 00:43:46.666
Madame said she wanted to follow your dad.

00:43:46.750 --> 00:43:48.916
-What should we do?
-I want to come with you.

00:43:49.000 --> 00:43:51.958
He embarrassed me in front of my friends.

00:43:53.125 --> 00:43:54.333
Take me with you, honey!

00:43:54.416 --> 00:43:55.375
Hello?

00:43:59.208 --> 00:44:00.208
You are cruel!

00:44:01.000 --> 00:44:02.125
Mom.

00:44:02.208 --> 00:44:03.458
You're so cruel, Raja.

00:44:04.000 --> 00:44:05.208
You are!

00:44:06.750 --> 00:44:07.583
Another revision?

00:44:08.666 --> 00:44:09.625
All right, sir.

00:44:18.083 --> 00:44:18.958
Mom.

00:44:19.500 --> 00:44:22.375
You embarrassed me in front of my friends.

00:44:22.458 --> 00:44:25.250
You said I'm not loyal to your father.

00:44:25.333 --> 00:44:30.416
You actually dared to point in my face
in front of my friends.

00:44:31.041 --> 00:44:35.041
Mom, I was wrong,
please forgive me, Mom.

00:44:35.125 --> 00:44:36.541
I lost control.

00:44:37.916 --> 00:44:39.916
I'm not supposed to treat you like that.

00:44:40.000 --> 00:44:41.541
You're cruel, Raja.

00:44:42.541 --> 00:44:43.625
You are cruel!

00:44:47.083 --> 00:44:48.500
-I know.
-Just go!

00:44:49.750 --> 00:44:50.666
All right, Mom.

00:44:53.041 --> 00:44:54.291
You are cruel, Raja.

00:44:55.500 --> 00:44:57.416
Yes, I know.

00:44:57.500 --> 00:44:58.750
I was wrong and cruel.

00:45:00.750 --> 00:45:03.166
I deserve to be punished.

00:45:09.166 --> 00:45:12.791
And I won't stop until you forgive me.

00:45:15.500 --> 00:45:18.208
Go away!

00:45:18.291 --> 00:45:20.083
Take your wife with you,

00:45:20.166 --> 00:45:21.708
the one you're always defending.

00:45:23.458 --> 00:45:25.125
You better go!

00:45:25.208 --> 00:45:26.666
If you don't go…

00:45:27.416 --> 00:45:31.416
You won't find me breathing tomorrow.

00:45:34.541 --> 00:45:35.458
Mom.

00:46:13.458 --> 00:46:14.291
Honey.

00:46:19.000 --> 00:46:20.625
How is she?

00:46:22.583 --> 00:46:23.583
Honey?

00:46:25.500 --> 00:46:26.833
Honey…

00:46:29.125 --> 00:46:31.125
Honey, what's wrong with your hand?

00:46:34.291 --> 00:46:35.666
What happened?

00:46:38.416 --> 00:46:39.583
Where is Nicholas?

00:46:42.000 --> 00:46:44.625
He is there.

00:46:45.458 --> 00:46:46.416
What happened?

00:46:48.791 --> 00:46:50.000
Get him prepared.

00:46:51.708 --> 00:46:53.916
We'll leave this house tonight.

00:47:18.541 --> 00:47:19.500
Mom.

00:47:24.750 --> 00:47:27.083
You told Raja to leave this house?

00:47:28.458 --> 00:47:29.916
Did you just kick us out?

00:47:31.625 --> 00:47:33.041
That's what you want, right?

00:47:33.708 --> 00:47:34.791
Are you satisfied now?

00:47:35.833 --> 00:47:36.666
You win.

00:47:37.583 --> 00:47:39.083
You took my son away!

00:47:40.291 --> 00:47:41.541
What do you mean?

00:47:43.083 --> 00:47:44.416
What are you even saying?

00:47:44.958 --> 00:47:47.375
There's no such competition here.

00:47:49.791 --> 00:47:50.750
Mom.

00:47:51.625 --> 00:47:54.791
All this time
I thought of you as my own mother.

00:47:55.666 --> 00:47:57.250
I love you dearly.

00:47:58.125 --> 00:48:01.291
I respect you like my own mother.

00:48:01.375 --> 00:48:03.250
No need to pretend.

00:48:03.333 --> 00:48:05.041
You're full of drama!

00:48:07.416 --> 00:48:10.875
You should be grateful you're even living
in my palace.

00:48:11.875 --> 00:48:12.958
A Frog Palace?

00:48:13.833 --> 00:48:14.958
The Frog Queen!

00:48:18.750 --> 00:48:20.041
What?

00:48:24.750 --> 00:48:26.541
You said I'm the Frog Queen?

00:48:26.625 --> 00:48:27.708
That's not me. It's…

00:48:27.791 --> 00:48:29.041
It's your voice!

00:48:29.125 --> 00:48:30.125
No, it wasn't me.

00:48:30.791 --> 00:48:31.958
Whatever!

00:48:32.041 --> 00:48:33.791
Call me the Frog Queen,

00:48:33.875 --> 00:48:37.291
or the Flying Head, the Jellyfish,
or the Gecko Queen.

00:48:37.375 --> 00:48:38.416
Whatever!

00:48:38.500 --> 00:48:39.750
Just go!

00:48:39.833 --> 00:48:40.833
Go away!

00:48:46.583 --> 00:48:47.958
-Dad.
-Yes, son.

00:48:48.041 --> 00:48:49.541
Where are we going?

00:48:53.250 --> 00:48:54.583
We are leaving this house.

00:48:55.208 --> 00:48:56.625
You can sleep.

00:49:23.625 --> 00:49:25.208
They are leaving.

00:49:25.875 --> 00:49:27.083
What should we do?

00:49:29.916 --> 00:49:33.708
-That's what I meant by "Bom Gom."
-Gomgom?

00:49:35.041 --> 00:49:35.875
Bomb.

00:49:36.458 --> 00:49:37.750
It has finally exploded.

00:49:39.458 --> 00:49:42.750
Andara and Raja
have finally left the house.

00:49:44.083 --> 00:49:47.750
I can't bear this.
It makes me so sad.

00:49:48.375 --> 00:49:50.791
It ended up like this.

00:49:52.458 --> 00:49:53.708
Apparently we're the bomb.

00:49:54.291 --> 00:49:56.791
Your voice was so loud.
She heard it.

00:49:56.875 --> 00:49:58.833
-What did I say?
-The frog queen.

00:49:58.916 --> 00:50:01.791
I didn't say it out loud,
I was whispering.

00:50:01.875 --> 00:50:03.583
I can't even hear my own voice.

00:50:05.333 --> 00:50:06.416
So, what now?

00:50:06.500 --> 00:50:07.750
Should we just admit it?

00:50:08.500 --> 00:50:10.458
What are you saying?

00:50:10.541 --> 00:50:12.291
You want to admit everything?

00:50:12.375 --> 00:50:13.958
Just let it be.

00:50:14.041 --> 00:50:17.500
They left this house and can afford
to buy a new one immediately.

00:50:17.583 --> 00:50:18.416
But us?

00:50:19.125 --> 00:50:21.625
-Yeah, that's true.
-We've just become her servants.

00:50:23.666 --> 00:50:25.750
You'll be cut into pieces
and fed to frogs.

00:50:25.833 --> 00:50:26.916
Do you want that?

00:50:27.000 --> 00:50:27.833
No.

00:50:27.916 --> 00:50:30.166
Nicholas, my grandson.

00:50:31.083 --> 00:50:33.541
Don't you go and leave me alone.

00:50:34.541 --> 00:50:37.708
I love you, Nicholas.

00:50:38.708 --> 00:50:40.000
Raja…

00:50:41.375 --> 00:50:43.666
Why did you leave me?

00:50:47.208 --> 00:50:49.958
Honey! Help me!

00:50:50.041 --> 00:50:51.916
Say something!

00:50:52.583 --> 00:50:53.833
Where's your voice?

00:50:57.666 --> 00:50:59.416
You're giving me a headache.

00:51:00.291 --> 00:51:01.791
You kicked them out.

00:51:03.291 --> 00:51:05.666
You're acting like a thug from the market.

00:51:06.250 --> 00:51:07.416
If you don't care!

00:51:08.000 --> 00:51:09.791
I'll rip your photo to shreds!

00:51:10.333 --> 00:51:11.583
I'm tired!

00:51:13.291 --> 00:51:14.958
You're so scary.

00:51:18.833 --> 00:51:21.416
Your behavior hasn't changed at all,
has it?

00:51:21.500 --> 00:51:22.458
I hate this!

00:51:22.541 --> 00:51:23.458
My goodness.

00:51:50.583 --> 00:51:51.416
Hi.

00:51:54.500 --> 00:51:55.500
Did you regret it?

00:52:01.791 --> 00:52:03.666
It's time to leave the house.

00:52:08.416 --> 00:52:09.875
And I didn't expect that…

00:52:11.291 --> 00:52:14.250
You can decorate this house
very beautifully.

00:52:21.000 --> 00:52:24.458
I want us to create happy days here.

00:52:25.708 --> 00:52:28.541
Perhaps to erase those dark days
in the Frog Palace.

00:52:32.583 --> 00:52:34.375
You're really poetic.

00:52:35.166 --> 00:52:36.625
Am I?

00:52:36.708 --> 00:52:39.875
Yes, even more romantic
than a writer like me.

00:52:39.958 --> 00:52:40.833
Seriously?

00:52:40.916 --> 00:52:42.041
Yes!

00:52:46.708 --> 00:52:47.541
Honey.

00:52:50.291 --> 00:52:52.708
You still have to visit Mom often, okay?

00:53:02.500 --> 00:53:04.833
How could Mom possibly forgive me?

00:53:07.208 --> 00:53:09.000
I am a disobedient child.

00:53:15.166 --> 00:53:21.166
A mother's love is much greater
than her anger.

00:53:22.583 --> 00:53:24.416
She will definitely forgive you.

00:53:42.625 --> 00:53:44.875
Yes, after this, I'll send the scenario.

00:53:44.958 --> 00:53:47.750
I'm busy making breakfast
for my son and husband.

00:53:48.625 --> 00:53:49.666
Eat first.

00:53:49.750 --> 00:53:50.583
My gosh.

00:53:54.166 --> 00:53:55.916
Mom, it's burnt.

00:53:57.625 --> 00:53:58.791
Burnt?

00:54:00.625 --> 00:54:01.458
Oh my…

00:54:02.416 --> 00:54:04.416
Let me order some bread first. One moment.

00:54:06.500 --> 00:54:07.541
Dear,

00:54:07.625 --> 00:54:09.125
I'm running late.

00:54:09.208 --> 00:54:11.333
Can you please take Nicho to school?

00:54:11.416 --> 00:54:12.541
I have a meeting.

00:54:13.583 --> 00:54:15.458
You want me to take him to school?

00:54:15.541 --> 00:54:18.541
All right, just go.

00:54:20.166 --> 00:54:21.291
Aren't you eating that?

00:54:22.791 --> 00:54:23.791
Give it to me then.

00:54:23.875 --> 00:54:24.791
It's burnt, Dad!

00:54:24.875 --> 00:54:25.750
It doesn't matter.

00:54:25.833 --> 00:54:27.291
It's a blessing from your Mom.

00:54:31.125 --> 00:54:31.958
Be good.

00:54:32.500 --> 00:54:33.833
-Bye, Dad!
-Bye!

00:54:34.750 --> 00:54:36.541
-Take care, honey!
-Sure, bye!

00:54:36.625 --> 00:54:37.458
Bye!

00:54:38.250 --> 00:54:40.583
I want Grandma's cooking.

00:54:41.708 --> 00:54:44.083
Because her cooking is really delicious!

00:54:45.166 --> 00:54:47.791
I'll order a burger for you
at school later.

00:54:48.500 --> 00:54:49.625
You like burger, right?

00:54:51.916 --> 00:54:53.416
Right, I'll order a taxi first.

00:54:55.250 --> 00:54:56.083
Gosh!

00:54:57.666 --> 00:54:58.708
Yes, sir?

00:54:58.791 --> 00:55:00.625
What are you doing?

00:55:00.708 --> 00:55:02.250
Where is the script?

00:55:03.083 --> 00:55:05.750
Don't wait any longer, send it now!

00:55:05.833 --> 00:55:07.458
Why are you so slow?

00:55:07.541 --> 00:55:09.375
I don't like this!

00:55:10.208 --> 00:55:11.416
Send it now!

00:55:11.500 --> 00:55:13.333
Okay, I'll send it now.

00:55:14.416 --> 00:55:15.500
Drink your milk!

00:55:17.125 --> 00:55:17.958
Oh, man…

00:55:24.333 --> 00:55:28.250
Donda, be careful when you look
for a daughter-in-law next time.

00:55:28.333 --> 00:55:31.500
-Don't choose the drama queen, it's scary!
-Indeed!

00:55:31.583 --> 00:55:34.916
That's possible, only if you haven't found
an in-law. What about me?

00:55:35.416 --> 00:55:36.875
But never mind. It's my house.

00:55:37.458 --> 00:55:38.791
-I'm in control here.
-Yes.

00:55:38.875 --> 00:55:40.875
-I refuse to be controlled.
-Correct!

00:55:40.958 --> 00:55:43.666
-Agreed!
-Especially with his wife.

00:55:43.750 --> 00:55:46.333
Andara and Raja, my son.

00:55:47.583 --> 00:55:50.291
What's that look for?
You look like a ghost. What is it?

00:55:53.083 --> 00:55:53.916
Mom.

00:55:54.583 --> 00:55:55.750
Donda.

00:55:55.833 --> 00:55:56.958
Raja.

00:55:58.166 --> 00:55:59.000
What is it?

00:56:04.791 --> 00:56:07.083
I just wanted to see how you're doing.

00:56:11.750 --> 00:56:13.375
I'm doing fine.

00:56:13.458 --> 00:56:14.458
As you can see.

00:56:15.083 --> 00:56:17.541
I exercise.

00:56:18.333 --> 00:56:19.625
I dance.

00:56:19.708 --> 00:56:21.875
But it's not tacky dancing like you said.

00:56:26.916 --> 00:56:27.833
I was wrong.

00:56:34.166 --> 00:56:35.708
Don't forget to eat, okay, Mom?

00:56:39.000 --> 00:56:39.833
I won't.

00:56:44.916 --> 00:56:45.916
I'm going then.

00:57:10.375 --> 00:57:11.666
Actually…

00:57:12.208 --> 00:57:16.208
My son Raja, he still loves me.

00:57:18.791 --> 00:57:19.833
Do you have a tissue?

00:57:22.333 --> 00:57:24.416
…THEN HE SLAPPED ANDIEN WITH…

00:57:29.416 --> 00:57:33.041
Oh, my, it's so late.

00:57:33.125 --> 00:57:35.375
My goodness! I forgot to order a taxi.

00:57:40.708 --> 00:57:42.750
Nicho.

00:57:42.833 --> 00:57:43.666
Son.

00:57:43.750 --> 00:57:44.833
Wake up, son.

00:57:44.916 --> 00:57:46.250
Wake up, son.

00:57:46.333 --> 00:57:48.041
It's already 8:00 a.m.

00:57:48.125 --> 00:57:49.416
Come on, you're late.

00:57:49.500 --> 00:57:51.041
I'll talk to the teacher later.

00:57:51.125 --> 00:57:53.083
Hurry up!

00:57:53.166 --> 00:57:54.416
Here!

00:57:55.541 --> 00:57:56.625
Let's go!

00:58:00.208 --> 00:58:01.125
Come on, dear!

00:58:05.541 --> 00:58:07.000
Auntie.

00:58:07.083 --> 00:58:08.125
What is it?

00:58:08.916 --> 00:58:09.958
Water is out.

00:58:11.083 --> 00:58:13.458
Madame, the gas is out.

00:58:14.208 --> 00:58:15.875
You two…

00:58:16.583 --> 00:58:18.041
Go ask Andara!

00:58:19.166 --> 00:58:20.916
Andara is no longer living here.

00:58:22.166 --> 00:58:24.416
You guys need to save up then!

00:58:25.791 --> 00:58:30.083
If you're so thirsty, go drink the water
from the fish pond!

00:58:30.166 --> 00:58:31.166
And you.

00:58:31.958 --> 00:58:33.666
Stop gassing it so hard!

00:58:34.875 --> 00:58:36.125
Slow down, hit the brakes!

00:58:36.666 --> 00:58:39.125
Or it'll spray out and splatter
all over your face.

00:58:39.875 --> 00:58:41.166
Let's find some firewood.

00:58:41.250 --> 00:58:44.583
It looks like there's firewood stocked up
in the woods next door.

00:58:47.958 --> 00:58:49.791
Andara, why are you so quiet?

00:58:49.875 --> 00:58:52.125
You look hypnotized.
Are you under a spell?

00:58:52.208 --> 00:58:53.333
Or did you get robbed?

00:58:55.166 --> 00:58:59.166
-Scripts have been arriving late recently.
-True.

00:58:59.750 --> 00:59:01.125
I'm sorry.

00:59:01.208 --> 00:59:04.708
It actually makes my work
even more difficult.

00:59:05.333 --> 00:59:07.583
Well, you know
what my mother-in-law is like.

00:59:08.541 --> 00:59:10.291
Ever since I left that house,

00:59:10.833 --> 00:59:12.666
I've been so exhausted.

00:59:12.750 --> 00:59:14.541
Really. Everything is in disarray.

00:59:14.625 --> 00:59:17.875
Housework, children, husband,
nothing is done.

00:59:18.416 --> 00:59:19.750
I can't cook either.

00:59:20.625 --> 00:59:22.875
Even my own son doesn't like my cooking.

00:59:22.958 --> 00:59:24.083
He said it's burnt!

00:59:26.375 --> 00:59:27.958
Whatever. Never mind.

00:59:28.041 --> 00:59:28.916
I'm so tired.

00:59:29.625 --> 00:59:33.500
Well, you know, in our line of work,
people just don't care.

00:59:33.583 --> 00:59:37.750
Whether you have a problem or not,
it doesn't matter at all.

00:59:37.833 --> 00:59:39.291
Anyway, for now… Hey!

00:59:42.000 --> 00:59:45.125
Let's make our series
number one in ratings!

00:59:45.208 --> 00:59:47.333
What if it gets stopped and wrapped?

00:59:47.416 --> 00:59:48.791
No money!

00:59:48.875 --> 00:59:49.875
No shopping!

00:59:49.958 --> 00:59:52.500
-No more eating gudeg.
-Can't go shopping, right?

00:59:53.333 --> 00:59:55.625
How long are we going to work like this?

00:59:55.708 --> 00:59:58.125
-Why are you even asking?
-"How long?"

00:59:58.208 --> 01:00:02.041
Andara as long as we need money,
we'll work until we get typhoid, jaundice.

01:00:02.125 --> 01:00:04.041
-Until we get moldy!
-Man! God forbid.

01:00:04.125 --> 01:00:06.000
Don't be like that!

01:00:06.083 --> 01:00:08.416
-No! God forbid.
-Gosh! Working yet complaining.

01:00:08.500 --> 01:00:10.750
-Or have no work and starve.
-No. Enough now.

01:00:10.833 --> 01:00:12.416
-All right, let's continue.
-Yes.

01:00:12.500 --> 01:00:14.083
Where were we with the synopsis?

01:00:14.916 --> 01:00:17.958
-There she is. All right then.
-You talk to her. No, you!

01:00:19.958 --> 01:00:21.500
What's wrong with this?

01:00:22.250 --> 01:00:24.458
Hello, Auntie. Hello.

01:00:25.083 --> 01:00:26.333
What is it?

01:00:26.416 --> 01:00:27.875
-Aunty Donda.
-Yes?

01:00:28.583 --> 01:00:33.083
We have been working together
for a long time, right?

01:00:33.791 --> 01:00:34.625
So?

01:00:34.708 --> 01:00:35.958
It's not enough work?

01:00:36.791 --> 01:00:38.583
-Go dig a grave!
-Oh no.

01:00:38.666 --> 01:00:40.333
Drain that snake-infested river!

01:00:40.416 --> 01:00:42.416
Or you just go lift the Tampomas ship!

01:00:42.500 --> 01:00:43.875
Is that not enough?

01:00:45.375 --> 01:00:47.083
It's not that, Auntie.

01:00:47.166 --> 01:00:50.791
-Look, we've worked for you for years.
-Yeah.

01:00:50.875 --> 01:00:53.166
-How come we don't get paid?
-Yeah.

01:00:53.250 --> 01:00:56.541
Just straight to the point.
You need money, right?

01:00:56.625 --> 01:00:58.333
Who do you think you are?

01:00:58.416 --> 01:01:00.333
You've been living under my roof,

01:01:00.416 --> 01:01:02.291
eating my food for free.

01:01:02.375 --> 01:01:04.291
Just look at your belly, it's huge.

01:01:04.375 --> 01:01:05.833
Because of what?

01:01:05.916 --> 01:01:08.166
You stole my grandson's milk, didn't you?

01:01:08.250 --> 01:01:10.375
You're as huge as an elephant
from all that!

01:01:10.458 --> 01:01:11.833
Yet you're still ungrateful!

01:01:12.416 --> 01:01:13.250
Well…

01:01:13.333 --> 01:01:19.000
-But you promised us a salary.
-What?

01:01:19.083 --> 01:01:20.791
What, you think I just grow money?

01:01:20.875 --> 01:01:22.250
Oh, you two, really!

01:01:22.333 --> 01:01:25.000
I helped you! I brought you here
from the village!

01:01:25.083 --> 01:01:26.833
Should I take you back to the Bukit?

01:01:26.916 --> 01:01:27.833
Enough! Go!

01:01:27.916 --> 01:01:30.750
-But Auntie--
-What? Don't shout! Go away!

01:01:30.833 --> 01:01:31.875
Yes, yes!

01:01:31.958 --> 01:01:33.125
Going to the back now.

01:01:33.208 --> 01:01:34.375
Just go!

01:01:34.458 --> 01:01:35.708
She's stingy to the bone.

01:01:36.500 --> 01:01:37.333
Rembulan!

01:01:37.916 --> 01:01:41.875
Where are you?
Don't act like you didn't hear that!

01:01:41.958 --> 01:01:44.416
Are you deaf? Rembulan!

01:01:44.500 --> 01:01:45.500
Madame.

01:01:46.458 --> 01:01:48.958
Earlier, I saw her
with all those suitcases.

01:01:49.041 --> 01:01:50.916
She has work to do, doing a hair bun.

01:01:51.000 --> 01:01:52.458
How bold she is!

01:01:52.541 --> 01:01:54.625
She didn't even ask for my permission!

01:01:54.708 --> 01:01:56.250
She's invisible like a ghost!

01:01:56.333 --> 01:01:58.166
Never mind her.

01:01:58.666 --> 01:02:00.833
Now, you should clean yourself up.

01:02:00.916 --> 01:02:02.416
You smell like oil!

01:02:02.500 --> 01:02:03.666
We're about to go out.

01:02:03.750 --> 01:02:08.625
Raja is supposed to send me money today.

01:02:09.125 --> 01:02:11.375
So, we'll go shop at the supermarket.

01:02:11.458 --> 01:02:12.750
We'll buy diamonds!

01:02:12.833 --> 01:02:14.208
Oh, thank you, Madame.

01:02:14.291 --> 01:02:15.791
Not for you, it's for me!

01:02:16.458 --> 01:02:17.750
Why should I buy you some?

01:02:18.916 --> 01:02:21.666
Now go. Bathe yourself
in the water of seven flowers.

01:02:22.166 --> 01:02:24.583
-You smell like a graveyard.
-Oh, my goodness.

01:02:25.833 --> 01:02:26.916
Now?

01:02:28.375 --> 01:02:29.291
On the doomsday!

01:02:39.541 --> 01:02:40.375
Let's go.

01:02:41.458 --> 01:02:42.291
Let's go.

01:02:51.125 --> 01:02:52.833
Come on, let's go.

01:02:57.750 --> 01:02:58.666
Sumi!

01:03:00.458 --> 01:03:02.416
-Sumi!
-Yes, Madame.

01:03:02.500 --> 01:03:04.208
-You're such a slowpoke!
-Wait…

01:03:04.750 --> 01:03:08.041
Put on these glasses and hat first. Wait!

01:03:09.208 --> 01:03:10.458
What's been keeping you?

01:03:21.833 --> 01:03:22.791
Sumi!

01:03:23.583 --> 01:03:24.625
Hey, you!

01:03:25.333 --> 01:03:26.708
Why did you leave me?

01:03:27.291 --> 01:03:28.375
Did you fly?

01:03:28.458 --> 01:03:29.833
Or disappear?

01:03:31.208 --> 01:03:32.750
Who is the one who left?

01:03:33.375 --> 01:03:35.625
I've been the one left behind.

01:03:35.708 --> 01:03:37.250
Don't be so fussy!

01:03:37.333 --> 01:03:38.291
What are you doing?

01:03:38.916 --> 01:03:39.750
Washing clothes.

01:03:40.291 --> 01:03:41.750
See? Iced grass jelly.

01:03:41.833 --> 01:03:43.333
I'm parched, you know.

01:03:44.416 --> 01:03:45.833
I want some too, I'm thirsty.

01:03:45.916 --> 01:03:47.041
Give me some!

01:03:47.125 --> 01:03:47.958
Oh, I see.

01:03:49.041 --> 01:03:52.208
I walk, you ride.
But you're the thirsty one?

01:03:52.291 --> 01:03:53.833
Shut up!

01:03:57.375 --> 01:03:58.708
-Delicious.
-It's delicious.

01:03:58.791 --> 01:04:00.791
Give it to the horseman as well.

01:04:01.333 --> 01:04:02.916
-Oh, the horseman?
-Yes!

01:04:03.000 --> 01:04:04.791
Sure, why not for the horse too?

01:04:04.875 --> 01:04:06.791
Do you want to try it?

01:04:06.875 --> 01:04:09.666
You worry about the horse,
but not me. I'm fine by myself.

01:04:09.750 --> 01:04:10.875
Don't be a nag!

01:04:10.958 --> 01:04:12.500
-Give me two more.
-Hurry up!

01:04:17.458 --> 01:04:19.375
Gosh, this kind of work is so hard!

01:04:19.458 --> 01:04:21.208
What is it now, Sumi?

01:04:22.166 --> 01:04:23.916
I'm sick of hearing your voice!

01:04:24.000 --> 01:04:26.083
Because of you, I forgot to wave.

01:04:26.166 --> 01:04:30.083
You're getting on my nerves, you know?

01:04:30.166 --> 01:04:32.208
Don't start with me.

01:04:33.166 --> 01:04:34.583
I'm sick of hearing you!

01:04:42.833 --> 01:04:45.458
-Down that side. okay.
-Whatever, I'm just getting off!

01:04:45.541 --> 01:04:47.750
It's all messy because of you.

01:04:47.833 --> 01:04:50.333
-Why blame me? Sir, find a parking spot.
-Okay.

01:04:52.500 --> 01:04:54.625
Call your boss, David.

01:04:54.708 --> 01:04:55.875
Donda!

01:04:55.958 --> 01:04:57.500
-Hey, David!
-Hello!

01:04:57.583 --> 01:04:59.000
Gosh, I miss you.

01:04:59.083 --> 01:05:02.666
-Oh, you, David!
-I miss you!

01:05:02.750 --> 01:05:05.166
-Go on!
-I want to buy diamonds.

01:05:05.250 --> 01:05:06.916
Please help me find the best one.

01:05:07.000 --> 01:05:09.458
For you, try something like this, okay?

01:05:09.541 --> 01:05:10.416
Here, take this.

01:05:10.500 --> 01:05:11.458
-Wait!
-Which one?

01:05:11.541 --> 01:05:14.500
I've had my eye on something
since last week. Where?

01:05:14.583 --> 01:05:16.833
-This is it, I think.
-Bring it, here.

01:05:16.916 --> 01:05:18.791
-Hurry up! Work faster!
-You can try it.

01:05:18.875 --> 01:05:20.125
Let's take it out.

01:05:20.208 --> 01:05:21.583
What's wrong with her?

01:05:21.666 --> 01:05:22.541
Oh, so pretty!

01:05:22.625 --> 01:05:25.083
Look, it's so pretty on your finger.

01:05:25.166 --> 01:05:26.291
It's glowing!

01:05:26.375 --> 01:05:28.333
-I'll take this one, pay quickly!
-Okay.

01:05:28.416 --> 01:05:30.250
How much is this?
Give me the card.

01:05:31.833 --> 01:05:33.333
Special price for you.

01:05:33.416 --> 01:05:34.708
-How much?
-Ten percent.

01:05:35.208 --> 01:05:36.833
You're really stingy!

01:05:36.916 --> 01:05:38.166
You make a lot of profit!

01:05:38.250 --> 01:05:41.083
You never give me a better deal.
How about 5%?

01:05:41.166 --> 01:05:43.833
-Always 10%. I'm bored of hearing it.
-10% is big.

01:05:43.916 --> 01:05:44.916
It's a great deal.

01:05:45.000 --> 01:05:46.791
-But not like that.
-Come on.

01:05:46.875 --> 01:05:48.416
-I'm a regular!
-Put it back.

01:05:48.500 --> 01:05:49.791
-5% okay?
-Stay calm.

01:05:49.875 --> 01:05:52.000
-Calm down.
-You talk too much.

01:05:52.083 --> 01:05:54.083
You're so good at joking.
I really like it!

01:05:55.833 --> 01:05:57.000
-All right.
-Pay now?

01:05:57.083 --> 01:05:59.041
-Hurry up!
-Wait. Here.

01:05:59.125 --> 01:06:00.500
Why is your hand shaking?

01:06:02.000 --> 01:06:04.541
-Not used to all this sparkle.
-Here's my card.

01:06:04.625 --> 01:06:06.666
This is a health insurance card.

01:06:07.708 --> 01:06:09.041
-Oh, you, Sumi!
-Sorry.

01:06:09.125 --> 01:06:10.500
Why did you give this to me?

01:06:11.208 --> 01:06:12.708
I'm sorry, Madam.

01:06:13.375 --> 01:06:15.083
-Is this the one?
-This is it.

01:06:15.166 --> 01:06:17.958
-I have bad eyesight.
-It's correct. Indri, bring it here.

01:06:22.583 --> 01:06:23.708
Here, your pin, please.

01:06:24.208 --> 01:06:25.666
-Move!
-You're so fierce.

01:06:25.750 --> 01:06:26.833
Don't look!

01:06:28.791 --> 01:06:30.000
Done. Take a look.

01:06:31.500 --> 01:06:33.166
-Declined.
-What's that mean?

01:06:33.250 --> 01:06:34.083
Declined.

01:06:34.166 --> 01:06:36.833
-I don't understand.
-It's rejected, Donda!

01:06:36.916 --> 01:06:39.500
-So, what should I do?
-Let's try one more time, okay?

01:06:39.583 --> 01:06:40.708
Gosh, Donda.

01:06:42.750 --> 01:06:44.791
Put your pin slowly. Remember carefully.

01:06:44.875 --> 01:06:45.708
-Move.
-Okay.

01:06:47.708 --> 01:06:50.000
There.
Take a look first.

01:06:50.083 --> 01:06:51.083
-Declined, okay?
-Why?

01:06:51.583 --> 01:06:52.583
Just say it!

01:06:52.666 --> 01:06:53.666
What's that mean?

01:06:53.750 --> 01:06:54.750
Give me another card.

01:06:55.458 --> 01:06:56.666
No other cards.

01:06:56.750 --> 01:06:58.083
-Really?
-Are there any?

01:06:58.166 --> 01:06:59.375
No, Madame.

01:06:59.458 --> 01:07:00.416
Hand me my phone.

01:07:00.500 --> 01:07:01.708
Here you go, Madame.

01:07:02.666 --> 01:07:04.208
There's no way, it's impossible!

01:07:04.291 --> 01:07:05.541
I have a lot money!

01:07:05.625 --> 01:07:09.416
-My son always puts money into my account.
-But it's declined. And what's this?

01:07:10.166 --> 01:07:12.958
-How come he hasn't sent me money?
-The card, sir. Thanks

01:07:14.250 --> 01:07:16.166
-Good Morning.
-Morning

01:07:23.000 --> 01:07:24.375
-Hello?
-Hello.

01:07:25.125 --> 01:07:26.083
Hello, Donda.

01:07:26.166 --> 01:07:27.458
What's your name again?

01:07:28.583 --> 01:07:29.416
Tomsa.

01:07:30.208 --> 01:07:31.375
Hey, you!

01:07:31.458 --> 01:07:33.208
How dare you!

01:07:33.291 --> 01:07:36.333
Don't tell me
you've taken my son's salary.

01:07:36.875 --> 01:07:39.375
Why hasn't it hit my account yet?

01:07:39.458 --> 01:07:42.000
I didn't receive any. Come on.

01:07:42.875 --> 01:07:44.583
I've already sent it.

01:07:45.333 --> 01:07:46.666
To Nicho's mom last week.

01:07:46.750 --> 01:07:47.625
What?

01:07:47.708 --> 01:07:48.583
To Andara?

01:07:49.333 --> 01:07:52.083
You're crazy. Why did you send it to her?

01:07:52.166 --> 01:07:55.708
Have you already forgotten whose son
Raja is?

01:07:55.791 --> 01:07:58.666
If he hadn't helped you, you'd be dead!

01:07:58.750 --> 01:08:01.541
Why did you say that?

01:08:01.625 --> 01:08:04.166
-Enough! I'm sick of you!
-All right then.

01:08:08.666 --> 01:08:10.708
Why did he send it to Andara?

01:08:10.791 --> 01:08:12.500
He's really getting on my nerves!

01:08:13.000 --> 01:08:14.958
-Let's go.
-Hey, where are you going?

01:08:15.041 --> 01:08:17.750
-What?
-Don't take my ring.

01:08:19.875 --> 01:08:21.416
Why is it so difficult?

01:08:22.625 --> 01:08:23.625
I hate it!

01:08:23.708 --> 01:08:25.041
There, there.

01:08:26.541 --> 01:08:27.791
-What?
-This.

01:08:27.875 --> 01:08:32.250
My dental plaque is worth more
than your entire self-esteem!

01:08:33.208 --> 01:08:36.250
-Let's go, Sumi! Don't be too slow.
-Yes, Madame.

01:08:37.000 --> 01:08:37.833
Raja.

01:08:39.291 --> 01:08:40.125
Yes, Uncle.

01:08:40.750 --> 01:08:42.708
Raja, your Mom just called me.

01:08:44.250 --> 01:08:45.500
My ear bleeds.

01:08:46.791 --> 01:08:49.166
What's going on between you and your Mom?

01:08:50.583 --> 01:08:53.583
You were the one who requested
the transfer to Andara.

01:08:55.500 --> 01:08:57.333
You're hiding something.

01:09:01.208 --> 01:09:03.083
There's definitely something going on.

01:09:15.708 --> 01:09:17.583
Just do your work properly.

01:09:17.666 --> 01:09:18.541
Yes, sir.

01:09:19.500 --> 01:09:20.625
Where is the report?

01:09:22.833 --> 01:09:23.666
Have you sent it?

01:09:27.291 --> 01:09:28.333
Andara!

01:09:29.291 --> 01:09:30.250
Wait…

01:09:30.333 --> 01:09:31.166
Mom.

01:09:32.875 --> 01:09:33.708
Mom.

01:09:34.333 --> 01:09:36.791
You! You took my son away from me!

01:09:37.958 --> 01:09:39.291
You stole my money!

01:09:39.375 --> 01:09:40.583
You are indeed…

01:09:40.666 --> 01:09:42.625
What kind of daughter-in-law are you?

01:09:42.708 --> 01:09:43.833
What do you mean?

01:09:43.916 --> 01:09:45.125
What do I mean, you said?

01:09:45.208 --> 01:09:47.916
My son's money is mine!

01:09:48.000 --> 01:09:51.166
Instead, you asked my son to transfer it
to your account!

01:09:51.916 --> 01:09:53.291
Oh, it's you!

01:09:53.375 --> 01:09:54.500
Do you have manners?

01:09:55.875 --> 01:09:57.541
Mom, It must be a misunderstanding.

01:09:57.625 --> 01:09:58.500
Like what?

01:09:58.583 --> 01:09:59.875
-Let me explain--
-Enough!

01:09:59.958 --> 01:10:01.541
I don't want to hear your voice!

01:10:02.375 --> 01:10:04.500
I'll pull your tongue out!

01:10:05.291 --> 01:10:06.750
I'll rip your vocal cords out!

01:10:07.416 --> 01:10:08.250
Understand?

01:10:09.666 --> 01:10:11.125
I hate you!

01:10:11.958 --> 01:10:13.791
-Mom, Mom.
-Where's my shoes?

01:10:13.875 --> 01:10:15.958
-Here, Mom.
-Stop it! Get off me! Move!

01:10:23.125 --> 01:10:24.166
Shameless!

01:10:25.041 --> 01:10:26.250
Oh my…

01:10:26.333 --> 01:10:27.250
My goodness!

01:10:28.541 --> 01:10:29.958
Why is it always me?

01:10:38.083 --> 01:10:42.000
Now's the time to take her treasure
while she's away.

01:10:44.708 --> 01:10:46.583
Are you sure we should take all this?

01:10:46.666 --> 01:10:49.041
Why are you asking?

01:10:49.583 --> 01:10:50.666
Obviously.

01:10:51.208 --> 01:10:53.083
We are not stealing, here.

01:10:53.166 --> 01:10:55.916
We're just taking our pay, our salary.

01:10:56.000 --> 01:10:57.208
Understand?

01:10:57.291 --> 01:10:59.416
-Agreed, just like Robin Hood, right?
-You…

01:10:59.500 --> 01:11:01.958
-We're taking what is rightfully ours.
-Exactly!

01:11:02.041 --> 01:11:04.083
My gosh, look at all of this.

01:11:04.666 --> 01:11:06.541
Third year, fourth year…

01:11:06.625 --> 01:11:08.041
How about this, honey? Look.

01:11:10.000 --> 01:11:11.833
-Not bad, honey.
-Right.

01:11:11.916 --> 01:11:13.916
Hurry! Don't leave anything behind.

01:11:14.000 --> 01:11:15.166
She's doomed!

01:11:15.250 --> 01:11:17.500
There are still so many
of her treasures here.

01:11:19.208 --> 01:11:21.208
-I'm sorry, Uncle.
-Forgive me, Uncle.

01:11:21.291 --> 01:11:23.083
It's our rights. Not stealing.

01:11:23.958 --> 01:11:26.958
Honey!

01:11:27.041 --> 01:11:30.083
-I really want to wear that.
-Do you?

01:11:30.166 --> 01:11:31.291
Let's see.

01:11:33.416 --> 01:11:35.708
-It suits you better.
-Right?

01:11:35.791 --> 01:11:39.750
Do we already look like rich people?
Rich people, hon.

01:11:44.333 --> 01:11:46.000
Dad's home.

01:11:46.083 --> 01:11:47.416
Dad!

01:11:48.125 --> 01:11:49.291
Hey.

01:11:49.375 --> 01:11:50.791
Staying in all day?

01:11:55.458 --> 01:11:56.666
Hi, dear.

01:11:58.750 --> 01:12:00.583
Why are you frowning?

01:12:05.041 --> 01:12:07.166
Dad, Grandma came here earlier.

01:12:08.750 --> 01:12:10.875
Grandma must be missing you.

01:12:10.958 --> 01:12:12.375
Not that.

01:12:12.458 --> 01:12:15.375
She is angry with Mom.

01:12:17.250 --> 01:12:18.750
Play with your dad, okay?

01:12:29.791 --> 01:12:32.416
Here, play with the T-Rex, okay?

01:12:33.958 --> 01:12:34.791
One moment.

01:12:48.708 --> 01:12:50.000
What's wrong with my mom?

01:12:52.125 --> 01:12:53.875
Did you send your salary to me?

01:12:55.750 --> 01:12:56.583
Yes.

01:12:57.250 --> 01:12:58.541
Why?

01:12:59.541 --> 01:13:00.625
Why?

01:13:00.708 --> 01:13:02.375
You asked.

01:13:02.458 --> 01:13:05.000
You want to get a taste of what I earn,
right?

01:13:05.083 --> 01:13:06.000
Who asked for it?

01:13:06.916 --> 01:13:08.583
I never did.

01:13:09.500 --> 01:13:13.208
I told you, I never got a taste
of your salary.

01:13:13.291 --> 01:13:15.333
But that doesn't mean I'm asking for it.

01:13:15.416 --> 01:13:17.000
I'm giving in.

01:13:17.791 --> 01:13:21.291
Now because you sent me the salary,
I'm the one getting blamed.

01:13:21.375 --> 01:13:23.000
She is angry.

01:13:23.666 --> 01:13:24.791
It's always my fault.

01:13:27.708 --> 01:13:30.041
And I'm stuck in the middle.

01:13:32.041 --> 01:13:34.166
I can't choose between you and my mother.

01:13:34.916 --> 01:13:37.500
You two are the women I love the most.

01:13:38.000 --> 01:13:41.083
Who asked you to choose?

01:13:42.583 --> 01:13:44.833
I never asked you to.

01:13:45.708 --> 01:13:48.375
I get it, I understand our situation.

01:13:55.500 --> 01:13:58.500
Don't ever send your salary to me again.

01:14:01.958 --> 01:14:03.541
I still have a lot of deadlines.

01:14:04.375 --> 01:14:05.333
Take care of Nicho.

01:14:15.416 --> 01:14:16.750
Sumi!

01:14:18.833 --> 01:14:19.833
Sumi!

01:14:19.916 --> 01:14:20.833
Yes, Madame.

01:14:20.916 --> 01:14:21.875
What's wrong?

01:14:21.958 --> 01:14:23.208
Where are my earrings?

01:14:23.291 --> 01:14:24.583
My ear studs?

01:14:24.666 --> 01:14:27.333
They're not here. All gone!

01:14:27.416 --> 01:14:28.583
Look at these.

01:14:29.458 --> 01:14:30.750
Who took it?

01:14:32.375 --> 01:14:33.541
You took it all, huh?

01:14:34.041 --> 01:14:36.625
God is the Greatest! I didn't take them.

01:14:36.708 --> 01:14:37.666
No way!

01:14:38.250 --> 01:14:39.541
You definitely took it all!

01:14:39.625 --> 01:14:44.791
I swear on my ancestors,
I did not take them!

01:14:44.875 --> 01:14:45.875
Then who did it?

01:14:46.375 --> 01:14:47.458
Wait a minute.

01:14:48.000 --> 01:14:51.166
Gomgom and Sondang haven't been around
since yesterday.

01:14:52.583 --> 01:14:55.041
Impossible! Them? They're my people!

01:14:55.125 --> 01:14:56.958
Don't you ever dare accuse my family!

01:14:57.583 --> 01:14:58.791
You must have taken it!

01:14:58.875 --> 01:15:00.750
Me? Why me?

01:15:00.833 --> 01:15:02.166
Don't be ridiculous!

01:15:02.250 --> 01:15:04.250
You thief!

01:15:05.083 --> 01:15:10.166
-Why am I the one being accused?
-I never thought you'd do this to me.

01:15:10.250 --> 01:15:11.291
How could you!

01:15:11.958 --> 01:15:14.041
All gone!

01:15:15.375 --> 01:15:16.833
I can't sell this.

01:15:18.083 --> 01:15:20.083
My goodness gracious!

01:15:21.125 --> 01:15:22.666
Where are they?

01:15:23.541 --> 01:15:25.375
What a mess.

01:15:28.166 --> 01:15:29.333
Could it be that…

01:15:31.250 --> 01:15:34.083
Oh, Sumi is right.

01:15:35.916 --> 01:15:37.458
Left without saying goodbye.

01:15:38.041 --> 01:15:39.375
All my belongings are gone.

01:15:39.458 --> 01:15:43.916
Don't tell me they really did it.

01:15:45.250 --> 01:15:46.083
What's this?

01:15:50.791 --> 01:15:53.666
Thank you so much, Auntie.

01:15:53.750 --> 01:15:57.875
Our salaries for the last seven years
have been paid off completely.

01:15:57.958 --> 01:16:02.333
Always with love,
from Gomgom and Sondang.

01:16:03.958 --> 01:16:08.333
I've been living with thieves
this whole time!

01:16:10.166 --> 01:16:13.500
May you never be safe,
no matter where you go!

01:16:13.583 --> 01:16:16.208
You crushed my heart!
You're both evil!

01:16:16.291 --> 01:16:17.291
Have no shame!

01:16:21.083 --> 01:16:24.125
My devotion has been completely in vain.

01:16:25.041 --> 01:16:29.208
Leaving behind bad memories
just because of slander!

01:16:31.750 --> 01:16:33.083
Even though I'm a victim.

01:16:33.166 --> 01:16:34.583
Divide et impera!

01:16:38.166 --> 01:16:40.000
Goodbye, Madame.

01:16:40.083 --> 01:16:42.250
Goodbye, Frog Palace.

01:17:00.083 --> 01:17:01.000
MY HUSBAND BIRTHDAY

01:17:08.500 --> 01:17:10.000
It's my son's birthday.

01:17:12.583 --> 01:17:13.625
That's right.

01:17:14.166 --> 01:17:15.958
It's my son's birthday.

01:17:16.041 --> 01:17:17.333
Where's my phone?

01:17:19.125 --> 01:17:20.708
Where is my phone?

01:17:53.791 --> 01:17:56.500
Happy birthday, my dear husband.

01:17:57.583 --> 01:17:59.250
My honey.

01:18:02.875 --> 01:18:04.333
My Raja.

01:18:11.583 --> 01:18:14.583
May you live a long life, honey.

01:18:18.500 --> 01:18:21.500
I can't live without you.

01:18:23.416 --> 01:18:25.250
Stay healthy, honey.

01:19:05.166 --> 01:19:06.208
Raja!

01:19:06.291 --> 01:19:07.125
Yes, Mom?

01:19:08.458 --> 01:19:09.708
What's wrong with you?

01:19:10.416 --> 01:19:12.083
Did you forget what day today is?

01:19:14.291 --> 01:19:16.208
What day is it?

01:19:17.500 --> 01:19:20.250
It's your birthday, son.

01:19:20.333 --> 01:19:21.583
Did you forget?

01:19:23.000 --> 01:19:24.166
Where is your wife?

01:19:26.000 --> 01:19:27.666
She's asleep.

01:19:27.750 --> 01:19:30.375
Have you sliced the bread?
Or cut the cake?

01:19:30.458 --> 01:19:31.833
Maybe blow out the candles?

01:19:31.916 --> 01:19:32.875
Never mind.

01:19:33.583 --> 01:19:36.541
I'm past the age of blowing out candles.

01:19:38.583 --> 01:19:41.583
Just pray for me, okay?

01:19:41.666 --> 01:19:43.666
So, I can make you happy.

01:19:44.625 --> 01:19:46.416
You are the best, Mom.

01:19:48.250 --> 01:19:49.833
I love you.

01:19:51.583 --> 01:19:53.750
I still feel guilty
about what I did to you.

01:19:54.541 --> 01:19:56.166
Just forget it.

01:19:56.250 --> 01:19:58.291
You don't need to talk about that anymore.

01:19:59.166 --> 01:20:01.000
I've already forgotten all about it.

01:20:01.083 --> 01:20:05.250
I just want to say
happy birthday to you, Raja.

01:20:05.833 --> 01:20:09.250
Live a long life, always healthy, okay?

01:20:09.791 --> 01:20:12.500
May you, your child,
and your wife be happy.

01:20:13.250 --> 01:20:14.875
So, when are you coming here?

01:20:15.458 --> 01:20:17.250
I miss you very much.

01:20:17.791 --> 01:20:20.291
I will cook for you later.

01:20:20.833 --> 01:20:22.416
Your favorite food.

01:20:22.916 --> 01:20:25.875
Arsik fish, mashed cassava leaves
with torch ginger flower.

01:20:25.958 --> 01:20:27.250
You favorite.

01:20:28.583 --> 01:20:29.416
Thank you, Mom.

01:20:31.416 --> 01:20:32.916
Take care of your health, okay?

01:20:34.833 --> 01:20:36.125
I love you, Mom.

01:20:38.041 --> 01:20:39.875
I'll wait for you

01:20:39.958 --> 01:20:41.500
until you come here.

01:20:41.583 --> 01:20:44.333
I miss you so much.

01:20:45.458 --> 01:20:46.291
All right.

01:20:47.458 --> 01:20:49.041
I will be home soon.

01:20:50.708 --> 01:20:54.000
Take care, okay?

01:21:11.958 --> 01:21:16.166
-Happy birthday to you
-Happy birthday to Dad

01:21:16.250 --> 01:21:19.708
-Happy birthday, happy birthday
-Happy birthday, happy birthday

01:21:19.791 --> 01:21:22.708
-Happy birthday to Dad
-Happy birthday to Dad

01:21:23.333 --> 01:21:25.250
Why are we blowing candles?

01:21:25.333 --> 01:21:29.041
Of course, I've prepared it for you.

01:21:29.125 --> 01:21:30.125
Blow it first.

01:21:35.291 --> 01:21:36.708
Thank you, my dear.

01:21:36.791 --> 01:21:39.458
Happy birthday, my love.

01:21:40.208 --> 01:21:41.916
Thank you, my dear son.

01:21:42.000 --> 01:21:43.750
Happy birthday, Dad.

01:21:43.833 --> 01:21:44.791
Thank you.

01:21:46.833 --> 01:21:49.416
We'll have lunch together
with Mom later, okay?

01:21:51.041 --> 01:21:52.625
-Really?
-Yes.

01:21:52.708 --> 01:21:54.666
-I've booked the table already.
-Thanks.

01:21:54.750 --> 01:21:56.833
-Yay! We'll go to Grandma's house!
-Sure.

01:22:02.875 --> 01:22:03.708
What's wrong?

01:22:03.791 --> 01:22:04.958
Does it hurt?

01:22:05.041 --> 01:22:06.416
Not feeling well.

01:22:06.500 --> 01:22:08.708
Let's just go to the hospital
for a checkup.

01:22:08.791 --> 01:22:10.166
No, no need.

01:22:11.791 --> 01:22:12.958
Or maybe…

01:22:13.791 --> 01:22:15.541
God wants to take me today?

01:22:15.625 --> 01:22:17.166
Where are you going?
Can I come?

01:22:17.666 --> 01:22:18.791
Stop it.

01:22:19.333 --> 01:22:20.916
Don't say things like that.

01:22:21.000 --> 01:22:22.166
You too, Nicho.

01:22:22.833 --> 01:22:25.458
If you guys left me,
who else do I have?

01:22:25.541 --> 01:22:26.500
It's not funny.

01:22:26.583 --> 01:22:28.625
I don't want you to talk like that.

01:22:28.708 --> 01:22:30.125
Just kidding.

01:22:30.208 --> 01:22:32.208
-It's your birthday today.
-I know.

01:22:32.291 --> 01:22:34.583
Whatever you say, God hears as a prayer.

01:22:36.166 --> 01:22:39.250
-I don't want you to leave me too soon.
-All right.

01:22:40.083 --> 01:22:41.208
I'll prepare the car.

01:22:41.291 --> 01:22:42.833
I'll change my clothes, then.

01:22:42.916 --> 01:22:45.541
So that we can wear matching clothes.

01:22:46.416 --> 01:22:47.416
Good boy.

01:22:48.166 --> 01:22:49.166
Okay.

01:22:49.250 --> 01:22:51.083
-All right then. Sure.
-Let's go.

01:22:51.666 --> 01:22:54.750
You're smart. Our pictures
will look great later.

01:23:08.375 --> 01:23:09.333
Dad?

01:23:09.958 --> 01:23:10.791
Wait.

01:23:14.000 --> 01:23:14.833
Honey?

01:23:15.625 --> 01:23:16.458
Honey?

01:23:17.291 --> 01:23:18.791
Honey, what's wrong?

01:23:20.625 --> 01:23:21.666
Honey?

01:23:22.500 --> 01:23:23.541
Oh, my God, honey.

01:23:23.625 --> 01:23:26.291
Honey, what's wrong? Honey?

01:23:26.375 --> 01:23:27.666
Honey, wake up.

01:23:28.291 --> 01:23:30.958
This isn't funny.

01:23:31.041 --> 01:23:31.875
Honey…

01:23:35.583 --> 01:23:37.791
Dad! Wake up, Dad!

01:23:37.875 --> 01:23:39.375
Wake up!

01:23:40.041 --> 01:23:41.583
Help!

01:23:41.666 --> 01:23:43.375
Dad, wake up!

01:23:43.458 --> 01:23:45.083
Help!

01:23:45.166 --> 01:23:48.041
-Dad, wake up!
-Honey, no!

01:23:56.875 --> 01:23:57.791
Where's my son?

01:23:57.875 --> 01:23:59.166
My son, Raja.

01:24:01.083 --> 01:24:02.875
-Mom.
-Where is my son Raja?

01:24:02.958 --> 01:24:04.208
He's there, Mom.

01:24:05.250 --> 01:24:07.833
Doctor, where's my son Raja?

01:24:07.916 --> 01:24:09.375
How is my husband, Doctor?

01:24:09.458 --> 01:24:10.875
Ma'am, I'm sorry.

01:24:11.458 --> 01:24:14.125
He died on the way here.

01:24:14.208 --> 01:24:15.291
No way!

01:24:17.916 --> 01:24:20.083
-Honey…
-My son, Raja…

01:24:21.375 --> 01:24:22.541
Wake up, son!

01:24:22.625 --> 01:24:24.375
Wake up!

01:24:24.458 --> 01:24:26.625
-Wake up, my dear son.
-Dad.

01:24:26.708 --> 01:24:28.375
My handsome son.

01:24:28.458 --> 01:24:30.125
-Dad!
-Wake up, son.

01:24:30.208 --> 01:24:31.750
Honey, wake up.

01:24:32.541 --> 01:24:34.958
Why did you leave me, son?

01:24:35.041 --> 01:24:37.291
Doctor, wake him up.

01:24:38.125 --> 01:24:39.291
Bring him back!

01:24:40.166 --> 01:24:42.166
I'll give you my all!

01:24:43.333 --> 01:24:44.833
We are sorry, Ma'am.

01:24:46.125 --> 01:24:48.875
-Wake up, Dad!
-My son…

01:24:48.958 --> 01:24:51.708
-Don't leave me, Dad.
-Wake up, wake up!

01:24:51.791 --> 01:24:54.375
-Dad!
-I'm here, son…

01:24:54.458 --> 01:24:55.583
Wake up, my son…

01:24:56.458 --> 01:24:57.291
Wake up!

01:24:58.708 --> 01:25:01.833
-Wake up, my beloved son.
-Wake up, Dad…

01:25:01.916 --> 01:25:02.750
Wake up, son.

01:25:03.875 --> 01:25:05.958
Wake up, Dad! Wake up…

01:25:06.875 --> 01:25:08.375
Wake up, Raja!

01:25:08.458 --> 01:25:09.500
Dad, wake up…

01:25:38.541 --> 01:25:42.875
OUR DEEPEST CONDOLENCES ON THE PASSING OF
RAJA PARTOGI GULTOM

01:25:42.958 --> 01:25:44.208
FROM UNSURE EXPRESS CARGO

01:27:06.625 --> 01:27:09.416
Raja…

01:27:09.500 --> 01:27:11.708
I'm here to see you.

01:27:11.791 --> 01:27:16.250
You're the only one we had, Raja.
Why did you leave us?

01:27:17.250 --> 01:27:19.916
Raja… Why must this happen, sister?

01:27:20.000 --> 01:27:21.250
She's the killer!

01:27:21.875 --> 01:27:24.125
-She is the murderer!
-You can't say that.

01:27:24.208 --> 01:27:25.791
You killed my son!

01:27:25.875 --> 01:27:30.083
Look! Her eyes are dry!
Where are your tears?

01:27:30.166 --> 01:27:31.625
You can't say that to her.

01:27:31.708 --> 01:27:34.041
You are indeed the murderer of my son!

01:27:34.125 --> 01:27:37.666
I will never forgive you!

01:27:37.750 --> 01:27:39.833
Please don't do that.

01:27:39.916 --> 01:27:41.541
You are the murderer of my son!

01:27:42.875 --> 01:27:44.666
She is my son's murderer!

01:27:44.750 --> 01:27:48.125
-Enough now. Stay calm.
-She's fooling me.

01:27:48.208 --> 01:27:49.875
Look at her!

01:27:49.958 --> 01:27:51.708
No tears at all.

01:27:55.958 --> 01:27:56.791
Enough now.

01:28:01.083 --> 01:28:02.125
Help her!

01:29:09.375 --> 01:29:10.458
Stand up, Donda.

01:29:10.541 --> 01:29:11.833
Raja is gone.

01:29:12.958 --> 01:29:14.041
What?

01:29:14.125 --> 01:29:15.083
Here he is.

01:29:15.166 --> 01:29:16.500
Look at him.

01:29:17.583 --> 01:29:18.875
But he doesn't want to eat.

01:29:18.958 --> 01:29:20.708
I usually eat with him.

01:29:21.250 --> 01:29:24.000
He used to accompany me at the table
whenever I ate.

01:29:24.541 --> 01:29:27.291
Yes, he's there but he no longer eats.

01:29:27.375 --> 01:29:29.541
Why doesn't he want to eat?

01:29:29.625 --> 01:29:30.958
Does he have a toothache?

01:29:31.041 --> 01:29:33.791
No, he's a healthy kid,
there's no way he's sick.

01:29:36.750 --> 01:29:40.166
Raja, wake up.

01:29:41.250 --> 01:29:43.458
Let's eat.

01:29:43.541 --> 01:29:46.041
I've made your favorite food.

01:30:30.791 --> 01:30:32.291
My child.

01:30:33.375 --> 01:30:35.208
My son…

01:30:47.875 --> 01:30:48.708
Nicho.

01:30:50.083 --> 01:30:53.416
You should eat, okay?

01:30:54.458 --> 01:30:55.625
Eat a lot.

01:30:58.125 --> 01:31:02.666
If your Dad were here,
he'd definitely want you to eat a lot.

01:31:04.541 --> 01:31:06.041
He wants you to be healthy.

01:31:07.375 --> 01:31:08.583
Come on, son.

01:31:08.666 --> 01:31:09.666
Eat a lot.

01:31:11.041 --> 01:31:14.250
My son is smart, right?

01:31:59.375 --> 01:32:00.958
Don't be sad, Mom.

01:32:01.041 --> 01:32:02.666
I'm here for you.

01:32:20.000 --> 01:32:22.083
I don't have any appetite anymore.

01:32:22.166 --> 01:32:23.708
Look at this.

01:32:31.083 --> 01:32:33.875
Frog, open your ears.

01:32:35.541 --> 01:32:37.500
Can you hear how sad my heart is?

01:32:38.291 --> 01:32:40.041
My son is no longer here.

01:32:49.500 --> 01:32:51.125
Oh, Raja…

01:32:52.291 --> 01:32:54.416
Why did you leave, son?

01:32:56.000 --> 01:32:58.333
I'm so sad.

01:32:59.500 --> 01:33:02.500
It breaks my heart, son.

01:33:22.083 --> 01:33:25.083
You knew it from the beginning

01:33:25.916 --> 01:33:28.250
We can't leave this house.

01:33:29.166 --> 01:33:31.166
I inherited it from my father.

01:33:33.041 --> 01:33:34.166
And what about my Mom?

01:33:34.833 --> 01:33:36.833
If we leave, she'll be all alone.

01:33:39.208 --> 01:33:40.041
Dear.

01:33:41.541 --> 01:33:43.625
For me,

01:33:44.583 --> 01:33:49.041
you are the best wife and the best mother.

01:33:52.250 --> 01:33:53.625
Please be patient.

01:34:08.791 --> 01:34:09.625
Mom.

01:34:10.666 --> 01:34:11.625
Grandma.

01:34:11.708 --> 01:34:12.541
Mom.

01:34:12.625 --> 01:34:13.708
Grandma?

01:34:16.875 --> 01:34:17.708
Mom?

01:34:21.708 --> 01:34:22.916
Mom.

01:34:23.000 --> 01:34:24.166
Grandma.

01:34:25.500 --> 01:34:28.916
-Mom?
-Mom, is she dead like Dad?

01:34:29.000 --> 01:34:30.041
What?

01:34:31.583 --> 01:34:33.708
Why would I die?

01:34:34.791 --> 01:34:36.083
Grandma!

01:34:42.541 --> 01:34:43.375
This side, Mom.

01:34:48.125 --> 01:34:49.666
So you guys are here.

01:34:52.875 --> 01:34:53.750
Yes, Mom.

01:34:54.708 --> 01:34:56.625
We missed you so much.

01:34:58.416 --> 01:34:59.791
Especially Nicholas.

01:35:00.916 --> 01:35:03.000
He asks for you every day.

01:35:03.708 --> 01:35:06.333
He said he couldn't wait to see you.

01:35:07.250 --> 01:35:09.000
This house is so quiet.

01:35:09.083 --> 01:35:10.750
They're all gone.

01:35:12.625 --> 01:35:13.916
Do you want to live here?

01:35:14.000 --> 01:35:15.541
Tell me.

01:35:16.458 --> 01:35:19.333
Mom, can we move back here?

01:35:19.416 --> 01:35:21.375
Please, Mom.

01:35:23.375 --> 01:35:26.375
Yay! We're moving to here again!

01:35:27.125 --> 01:35:28.958
Please forgive me.

01:35:29.041 --> 01:35:31.375
I'm selfish.

01:35:32.291 --> 01:35:34.083
I was always trying to win on my own.

01:35:34.791 --> 01:35:39.500
But I've realized Raja doesn't
belong to me alone.

01:35:43.541 --> 01:35:46.666
I should be the one apologizing to you.

01:35:48.333 --> 01:35:50.125
I'm sorry, Mom.

01:35:51.916 --> 01:35:53.041
You…

01:35:53.125 --> 01:35:56.250
Even though I have a sharp tongue,

01:35:56.750 --> 01:35:58.750
which often hurts your feelings.

01:35:59.916 --> 01:36:01.666
I truly care about you.

01:36:02.250 --> 01:36:03.791
I love my grandson.

01:36:04.916 --> 01:36:06.541
Don't ever leave me again.

01:36:06.625 --> 01:36:08.083
Promise me.

01:36:08.166 --> 01:36:09.083
Yes, Mom.

01:36:10.208 --> 01:36:11.833
I promise.

01:36:13.625 --> 01:36:16.625
I will learn to be a good daughter-in-law
for you.

01:36:20.125 --> 01:36:20.958
And, Mom…

01:36:23.250 --> 01:36:25.458
I want to serve you.

01:36:27.458 --> 01:36:30.416
As soon as I left this house, I realized…

01:36:31.500 --> 01:36:33.166
I need you.

01:36:34.625 --> 01:36:37.750
There's no one
to remind me to eat anymore.

01:36:37.833 --> 01:36:40.000
There's no one to discipline me.

01:36:40.916 --> 01:36:42.333
Manage me.

01:36:42.958 --> 01:36:44.583
My cooking isn't good.

01:36:44.666 --> 01:36:47.250
He didn't like it, saying it was burnt.

01:36:48.125 --> 01:36:49.666
That's why

01:36:50.208 --> 01:36:52.166
we need other people in this life.

01:36:53.583 --> 01:36:55.916
We should always stay together,
that's important.

01:37:01.250 --> 01:37:02.875
My daughter.

01:37:02.958 --> 01:37:04.666
Mom.

01:37:04.750 --> 01:37:06.833
You are my daughter.

01:37:06.916 --> 01:37:09.375
Don't ever leave me again.

01:37:12.208 --> 01:37:17.250
I can get rid of these wrinkles
without surgery using this product.

01:37:20.500 --> 01:37:21.875
Good night, honey.

01:37:22.666 --> 01:37:24.208
May you be happy with Raja.

01:37:27.333 --> 01:37:28.833
I'm so sad.

01:37:30.833 --> 01:37:32.250
Ever since you left us.

01:37:34.083 --> 01:37:35.125
But it's okay.

01:37:35.666 --> 01:37:37.208
You have Raja by your side now.

01:37:38.375 --> 01:37:41.458
You really like joking around.

01:37:47.416 --> 01:37:48.291
Yes, sir.

01:37:48.958 --> 01:37:52.250
I'm really sorry.

01:37:53.666 --> 01:37:56.125
I can't continue.

01:37:57.875 --> 01:38:03.375
Right now I have to focus on taking care
of my son and mother-in-law.

01:38:03.458 --> 01:38:06.291
And I'm planning to quit writing, sir.

01:38:09.958 --> 01:38:13.125
Hey, are you the director?

01:38:13.208 --> 01:38:14.791
-Hello, Ma'am.
-Producer.

01:38:14.875 --> 01:38:17.583
Hey, Mr. Producer.

01:38:17.666 --> 01:38:20.541
She actually wants to do this job.

01:38:20.625 --> 01:38:21.833
Only if…

01:38:22.500 --> 01:38:23.791
Well…

01:38:23.875 --> 01:38:26.750
You increase her salary, okay?

01:38:26.833 --> 01:38:28.458
So she can do her best.

01:38:29.000 --> 01:38:30.166
Increase her salary?

01:38:35.333 --> 01:38:36.583
You know.

01:38:37.083 --> 01:38:39.791
She is a new widow.

01:38:39.875 --> 01:38:41.041
It's still fresh.

01:38:41.666 --> 01:38:42.500
Got it, sir?

01:38:43.291 --> 01:38:45.041
We can discuss that.

01:38:46.166 --> 01:38:49.125
Just tell Andara to come to the office.
Okay, Ma'am?

01:38:49.208 --> 01:38:50.208
That's great.

01:38:50.291 --> 01:38:51.208
Great.

01:38:51.291 --> 01:38:53.958
Thank you, sir.

01:38:56.000 --> 01:38:57.500
I have no appetite.

01:38:58.250 --> 01:39:01.583
How can you feed your son
without any money?

01:39:02.791 --> 01:39:04.333
It's not like that, Mom.

01:39:04.416 --> 01:39:05.583
What is it then?

01:39:05.666 --> 01:39:10.291
I just don't want to make
the same mistake again.

01:39:10.375 --> 01:39:12.875
My dear, you're an adult.

01:39:13.500 --> 01:39:19.250
You are not a donkey,
who repeats its mistakes.

01:39:20.750 --> 01:39:21.791
Understand?

01:39:23.250 --> 01:39:25.458
Yes, Mom.

01:39:26.541 --> 01:39:27.375
Oh, yeah.

01:39:29.166 --> 01:39:30.666
Now I know.

01:39:30.750 --> 01:39:31.625
My mind is open.

01:39:31.708 --> 01:39:32.583
What?

01:39:33.708 --> 01:39:34.708
How about this?

01:39:36.541 --> 01:39:40.458
I'm so smart, stylish, and good at acting.

01:39:40.541 --> 01:39:42.125
I'm really good.

01:39:42.208 --> 01:39:44.625
You take a video later.

01:39:44.708 --> 01:39:48.083
And it will be shared everywhere
to those children these days.

01:39:48.166 --> 01:39:49.833
-Viral?
-Yeah, dancing.

01:39:49.916 --> 01:39:50.875
Something like that.

01:39:50.958 --> 01:39:52.458
I can cook.

01:39:52.541 --> 01:39:56.041
She is good at cooking, singing,
dancing, farming, and gardening.

01:39:56.708 --> 01:39:58.333
I can plant them all.

01:39:58.416 --> 01:40:01.375
Wherever it is. Right.

01:40:01.458 --> 01:40:03.375
Do you want to go viral?

01:40:03.458 --> 01:40:05.125
Yes. That's it,

01:40:05.208 --> 01:40:06.458
I want to be a celebrity.

01:40:06.541 --> 01:40:09.250
-Mom wants to be a celebrity?
-Exactly! Right.

01:40:09.333 --> 01:40:11.500
I know how to act.

01:40:11.583 --> 01:40:14.875
-I want you to record me, okay?
-Okay.

01:40:14.958 --> 01:40:17.125
-I'll go like this.
-Mom…

01:40:17.875 --> 01:40:21.083
Let's do it.
I can dance like this.

01:40:21.166 --> 01:40:23.708
I can sing.
I can strike a pose.

01:40:23.791 --> 01:40:24.958
Don't worry about it.

01:40:25.041 --> 01:40:26.500
I'm tired, need a rest.

01:40:31.458 --> 01:40:37.041
-Slow down.
-My hand! Be good, okay?

01:40:37.125 --> 01:40:38.250
I'm scared…

01:40:38.333 --> 01:40:40.291
I think the goat is scared too.

01:40:40.375 --> 01:40:42.833
-I know, but we have to do it.
-All right then.

01:40:42.916 --> 01:40:43.958
It's okay.

01:40:44.041 --> 01:40:45.791
Your life will be good here.

01:40:45.875 --> 01:40:48.458
Let's hope Auntie is willing
to take us back.

01:40:48.541 --> 01:40:51.083
She'll give you any name, just accept it.

01:40:51.166 --> 01:40:52.833
Hey, thieves!

01:40:52.916 --> 01:40:56.000
You guys are thieves!
Where do you think you're going?

01:40:59.500 --> 01:41:01.375
Oh, you're asking for trouble, huh!

01:41:03.541 --> 01:41:05.041
What's all that noise?

01:41:05.125 --> 01:41:07.375
You're a troublemaker!

01:41:08.000 --> 01:41:08.833
What happened?

01:41:11.208 --> 01:41:12.666
Hey, you!

01:41:14.708 --> 01:41:15.916
What are you doing here?

01:41:16.791 --> 01:41:18.416
Are you guys brainless, or what!

01:41:18.500 --> 01:41:20.375
That's right, you're thieves.

01:41:20.458 --> 01:41:22.041
Are you a person or a ghost?

01:41:22.125 --> 01:41:23.333
A person.

01:41:23.416 --> 01:41:24.958
Then, where's your brain?

01:41:25.041 --> 01:41:27.000
Where is everything you stole?

01:41:27.083 --> 01:41:28.125
Here, Auntie.

01:41:28.208 --> 01:41:29.541
It's now a goat.

01:41:29.625 --> 01:41:31.375
You're crazy!

01:41:31.875 --> 01:41:34.291
If I had known from the start
you were thieves,

01:41:34.375 --> 01:41:37.458
I would rip out your brains
and fold your intestines!

01:41:37.541 --> 01:41:39.583
-That's so scary.
-Please don't.

01:41:40.416 --> 01:41:41.666
Please forgive us.

01:41:41.750 --> 01:41:44.625
Hey, Andara, you came back.

01:41:44.708 --> 01:41:46.500
Sumi, why are you here?

01:41:47.583 --> 01:41:50.458
I asked her to come back.

01:41:50.541 --> 01:41:51.875
To help us at home.

01:41:52.625 --> 01:41:55.958
Did you know that she's the one
I accused?'

01:41:57.083 --> 01:41:57.916
Sis!

01:42:02.291 --> 01:42:03.125
Auntie.

01:42:07.083 --> 01:42:09.291
-Who are you?
-It's me, Rembulan.

01:42:14.208 --> 01:42:19.458
You once said, "I'll get a husband
who is on my level."

01:42:19.958 --> 01:42:21.791
But what is this?

01:42:22.458 --> 01:42:24.083
What do you mean?

01:42:24.166 --> 01:42:28.250
He's a security guard,
but that's just a part-time job.

01:42:28.333 --> 01:42:30.041
He's a musician.

01:42:30.125 --> 01:42:33.750
Songwriter, composer, singer.

01:42:33.833 --> 01:42:35.416
Well, there's another side job.

01:42:35.500 --> 01:42:38.208
-Dancing, like back then.
-I see.

01:42:38.708 --> 01:42:41.458
-But now he's only dancing with me.
-Only with you.

01:42:41.541 --> 01:42:43.375
You're showing off!

01:42:43.458 --> 01:42:46.375
You're so cheeky and flirtatious,
you're so clingy to him.

01:42:47.541 --> 01:42:49.916
You're basically want to move back in,
right?

01:42:50.000 --> 01:42:52.208
Yes, I used to be arrogant.

01:42:53.125 --> 01:42:54.958
But with Pongki here with me,

01:42:55.041 --> 01:42:59.208
my world that was once dark…

01:42:59.291 --> 01:43:02.708
is now blooming with color.

01:43:03.791 --> 01:43:07.458
Auntie Rembulan, how did you meet him?

01:43:07.541 --> 01:43:08.916
And get married so quickly?

01:43:09.000 --> 01:43:11.291
That's a really long story.

01:43:11.375 --> 01:43:13.791
The director cut it short.

01:43:13.875 --> 01:43:15.375
He said it was really wild.

01:43:15.458 --> 01:43:18.708
Wilder than what's in the videos.

01:43:18.791 --> 01:43:19.666
Which video?

01:43:20.666 --> 01:43:23.458
Where's the video, which one?

01:43:23.541 --> 01:43:24.750
What's in the video?

01:43:24.833 --> 01:43:28.416
-Let's see, how is it?
-Show it to us.

01:43:28.500 --> 01:43:30.875
-Not this one, oh this? Wait.
-Yes, that's okay.

01:43:33.541 --> 01:43:34.375
Oh, my!

01:43:35.541 --> 01:43:37.750
-Close his eyes. Close them.
-Don't look.

01:43:43.750 --> 01:43:44.583
Is it over?

01:43:46.541 --> 01:43:47.791
I think so.

01:43:49.416 --> 01:43:50.625
Not to be continued?

01:43:51.875 --> 01:43:53.416
How should I know?

01:43:54.791 --> 01:43:55.625
All right, then.

01:43:58.750 --> 01:43:59.958
Wow, so many.

01:44:00.041 --> 01:44:03.708
"You don't look old enough
to have a grandson."

01:44:04.916 --> 01:44:06.125
What do you mean?

01:44:06.208 --> 01:44:07.125
I look bad?

01:44:07.708 --> 01:44:09.666
Your eyes are crossed!

01:44:09.750 --> 01:44:11.541
I'm beautiful.

01:44:11.625 --> 01:44:13.375
Sorry not sorry.

01:44:13.458 --> 01:44:18.833
I am beautiful, because I always take care
of my skin and my face.

01:44:18.916 --> 01:44:23.500
My skin is glowing!

01:44:24.208 --> 01:44:26.416
Because I always use serum.

01:44:26.500 --> 01:44:28.416
The serum that always…

01:44:29.333 --> 01:44:30.666
Your eyeballs.

01:44:32.375 --> 01:44:37.541
My fish, thank you for always
accompanying the queen here.

01:44:37.625 --> 01:44:38.875
In this house.

01:44:38.958 --> 01:44:40.041
It got me wet!

01:44:41.125 --> 01:44:43.125
They're chatty today, huh?

01:44:43.208 --> 01:44:44.375
You naughty kids.

01:44:44.458 --> 01:44:45.583
You'll go to hell.

01:44:46.125 --> 01:44:50.375
"Mom, you look shiny."

01:44:51.208 --> 01:44:52.250
Of course.

01:44:53.541 --> 01:44:54.666
Morning and evening.

01:44:55.416 --> 01:44:56.500
Dusk and night.

01:44:57.041 --> 01:45:00.208
I'll arrive
before the vengeful ghost does.

01:45:01.166 --> 01:45:03.208
I always use this, darling.

01:45:03.833 --> 01:45:06.833
"My son-in-law is lazy,
should I whip him?"

01:45:06.916 --> 01:45:08.833
Whip him with a white whip, okay?

01:45:08.916 --> 01:45:11.375
If it's thundering rain, you whip him.

01:45:11.458 --> 01:45:14.625
If you don't whip him,
I'll whip him with a bull whip.

01:45:15.208 --> 01:45:16.833
So many questions.

01:45:18.583 --> 01:45:20.291
My cook is take a while then.

01:45:20.375 --> 01:45:21.208
Ouch! See?

01:45:23.083 --> 01:45:24.333
It's hot as well.

01:45:24.416 --> 01:45:25.750
For mothers,

01:45:28.041 --> 01:45:29.916
so that your husband will feel at home,

01:45:30.458 --> 01:45:34.583
in the bed of love, of marriage,

01:45:34.666 --> 01:45:37.250
so that it'll be an eternal provision.

01:45:37.333 --> 01:45:41.291
Don't forget to use these products. Okay?

01:45:41.375 --> 01:45:43.541
Here. This.

01:45:44.125 --> 01:45:48.250
This is the best product on earth,
MK Cosmetics.

01:45:50.375 --> 01:45:53.083
It's suitable for hot weather.

01:45:53.166 --> 01:45:54.958
The air here is nice, isn't it?

01:45:55.041 --> 01:45:56.458
It's not too hot.

01:45:56.541 --> 01:45:58.208
It's cool!

01:46:01.375 --> 01:46:03.791
So hot.

01:46:03.875 --> 01:46:06.166
Why is this world so hot?

01:46:06.250 --> 01:46:10.166
This is called MK Skin Cream.

01:46:10.250 --> 01:46:11.958
Skin, okay?

01:46:12.041 --> 01:46:13.791
MK Skin Cream.

01:46:14.458 --> 01:46:16.625
It's mating season for you, huh?

01:46:16.708 --> 01:46:18.416
Do you want a girl?

01:46:18.500 --> 01:46:20.708
I'll find you one later, my dear child.

01:46:21.250 --> 01:46:23.416
So your skin is as smooth as mine.

01:46:23.500 --> 01:46:25.333
Because I always use serum.

01:46:25.416 --> 01:46:28.708
Always use serum, so my skin is glowing.

01:46:28.791 --> 01:46:31.625
Night cream, day cream, dusk cream.

01:46:31.708 --> 01:46:35.375
Use these. okay, dear?

01:46:35.458 --> 01:46:39.291
All my darlings, all the children
of the queen, Frog Queen's child.

01:46:39.916 --> 01:46:41.291
Bye!

01:46:41.375 --> 01:46:45.708
Okay, I'm going for a walk
by the rice field.

01:46:49.250 --> 01:46:50.291
What?

01:46:50.375 --> 01:46:51.916
Go home!

01:46:52.500 --> 01:46:54.041
Go home!

01:46:54.125 --> 01:46:56.125
Watch out! Pickpocket!

01:46:56.208 --> 01:46:57.458
Go!

01:46:58.750 --> 01:47:01.708
Watch your belongings.

01:47:02.208 --> 01:47:04.458
Don't forget your kids!

01:47:04.541 --> 01:47:05.375
Sumi!

01:47:06.333 --> 01:47:07.166
Sumi!